{"version": "0.2.0-beta.6", "title": "Karakai Jouzu no Takagi-san", "title_uuid": "8b310d10-25a6-4fdb-aaef-cacc33c51c4b", "volume": "Karakai-Jouzu-Takagi-san-01", "volume_uuid": "2a70e057-6fd1-4d84-b5a6-a614306e397b", "pages": [{"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [766, 17, 828, 801], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["ハウハードの高木さんは山本製品"]}, {"box": [637, 1155, 819, 1176], "vertical": false, "font_size": 15.0, "lines": ["ＳＨＯＮＴＡＴＡＮＡＴＩＣＯＭＣＳＳＰＩＮＥ"]}], "img_path": "001.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [230, 44, 613, 85], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["ＧｏｔｏｍｅＸｔｐａｇｅ"]}, {"box": [234, 1110, 612, 1150], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["ＧｏｔｏｍｅＸｔｐａｇｅ"]}], "img_path": "002.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [66, 1101, 678, 1133], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["からかい上手の高木さん。山本宗一朗"]}], "img_path": "003.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [670, 528, 776, 543], "vertical": false, "font_size": 15.0, "lines": ["ｏｎｔｅｎｔｓ"]}, {"box": [721, 700, 743, 824], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["消しゴムっっ"]}, {"box": [582, 709, 603, 825], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["プール・"]}, {"box": [439, 720, 466, 824], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["変顔"]}, {"box": [302, 709, 324, 823], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["筋トレーニング"]}, {"box": [163, 712, 183, 773], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["空き缶"]}, {"box": [721, 973, 745, 1076], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["日直"]}, {"box": [583, 984, 603, 1002], "vertical": false, "font_size": 12.0, "lines": ["きゃあ"]}, {"box": [441, 973, 463, 1014], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["風邪"]}, {"box": [304, 957, 320, 1028], "vertical": true, "font_size": 16.0, "lines": ["本屋さん"]}], "img_path": "004.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [], "img_path": "005.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [107, 127, 132, 189], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["ふふ．．．"]}, {"box": [442, 410, 500, 570], "vertical": true, "font_size": 30.0, "lines": ["ねえ、", "西片。"]}, {"box": [330, 465, 384, 566], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["な、何！？", "高木さん！？"]}, {"box": [173, 457, 205, 567], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["何してんの？"]}, {"box": [323, 881, 380, 950], "vertical": true, "font_size": 29.0, "lines": ["別に．．．", "何も．．．"]}, {"box": [105, 880, 130, 946], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["ふーん。"]}], "img_path": "006.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [712, 250, 743, 304], "vertical": true, "font_size": 31.0, "lines": ["良い、"]}, {"box": [452, 80, 497, 200], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["あとはこれを", "箱に仕込めば、"]}, {"box": [550, 250, 575, 316], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["バネだ。"]}, {"box": [261, 94, 317, 210], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["ビックリ箱の", "完成さ。"]}, {"box": [182, 132, 210, 292], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["見てろよ高木さん。"]}, {"box": [594, 479, 683, 677], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["いっもいつも", "オレを", "からかいやがって。"]}, {"box": [82, 494, 179, 667], "vertical": true, "font_size": 27.0, "lines": ["今日こそオレが", "高木さんを", "からかってやる。"]}, {"box": [713, 853, 738, 913], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["んー"]}, {"box": [463, 857, 486, 956], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["どしたの？"]}, {"box": [335, 841, 415, 966], "vertical": true, "font_size": 30.0, "lines": ["いやー食畜が", "筆箱が", "あかなくって。"]}], "img_path": "007.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [694, 51, 743, 202], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["ゆがんじゃったの", "かなー、"]}, {"box": [617, 53, 660, 194], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["ちょっと西片", "あけてくんない？"]}, {"box": [436, 59, 494, 119], "vertical": true, "font_size": 28.0, "lines": ["あ、", "うん。"]}, {"box": [97, 83, 146, 199], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["なんだ、", "簡単にあく．．．"]}, {"box": [427, 467, 494, 528], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["！？"]}, {"box": [90, 419, 168, 677], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["うわぁ！！！"]}], "img_path": "008.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [647, 85, 700, 150], "vertical": true, "font_size": 29.0, "lines": ["なんだ", "西片。"]}, {"box": [474, 83, 550, 189], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["な、", "なんでも", "ありません。"]}, {"box": [413, 64, 431, 167], "vertical": true, "font_size": 16.0, "lines": ["くっくつく。"]}, {"box": [56, 82, 74, 146], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["．．．．．．．．"]}, {"box": [658, 514, 737, 638], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["西片って", "ホントいい", "反応するわー。"]}, {"box": [279, 495, 394, 573], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["うるさい", "なっ。"]}, {"box": [64, 500, 137, 602], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["くそ．．．また", "まんまと", "やられた。"]}, {"box": [194, 630, 235, 669], "vertical": false, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["ＨＸ"]}, {"box": [658, 877, 736, 1052], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["しかもオレが", "やろうとしたことを", "先に．．．"]}, {"box": [455, 874, 582, 996], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["そもそも", "高木さんが", "オレに助けを", "求めるなんて", "おかしいんだ。"]}, {"box": [208, 883, 287, 963], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["そこで", "気づけよ", "オレ．．．"]}, {"box": [66, 885, 115, 990], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["さすが", "高木さんだ。"]}], "img_path": "009.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [574, 87, 627, 209], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["次の手を", "考えなければ"]}, {"box": [448, 80, 506, 191], "vertical": true, "font_size": 27.0, "lines": ["どうすれば", "いい！？"]}, {"box": [111, 67, 199, 274], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["どうすれば", "高木さんを", "はずかしめられる！？"]}, {"box": [741, 835, 768, 888], "vertical": true, "font_size": 27.0, "lines": ["ねえ。"]}, {"box": [562, 843, 630, 904], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["な．．．何？"]}, {"box": [404, 823, 480, 966], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["消しゴム", "貸して、", "忘れちゃったの。"]}], "img_path": "010.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [531, 73, 632, 191], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["ははん！", "消しゴムを", "忘れるなんて", "ドジだねぇ。"]}, {"box": [429, 86, 451, 155], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["そーね。"]}, {"box": [372, 116, 401, 172], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["ありが"]}, {"box": [284, 111, 301, 175], "vertical": true, "font_size": 17.0, "lines": ["．．．．．．？"]}, {"box": [675, 526, 695, 604], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["うーん．．．"]}, {"box": [69, 522, 119, 621], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["そーいえば", "さー"]}, {"box": [37, 841, 118, 938], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["今考えると", "ホント子供", "だよなー。"]}, {"box": [455, 815, 613, 987], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["消しゴムに", "好きな人の", "名前書いて、", "使い切ったら", "両想いになれるって", "やつあったよね。"]}, {"box": [258, 834, 303, 966], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["あー、あったね", "そんなの。"]}], "img_path": "011.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [558, 93, 611, 181], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["ふーんことも", "子供ねー。"]}, {"box": [449, 83, 475, 162], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["へえー"]}, {"box": [724, 487, 747, 565], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["．．．．．．？"]}, {"box": [166, 499, 188, 614], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["なんだよ．．．"]}, {"box": [733, 792, 793, 939], "vertical": true, "font_size": 28.0, "lines": ["何も！！", "書いてないだろ。"]}, {"box": [395, 816, 421, 883], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["ほほー、"]}, {"box": [206, 815, 255, 895], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["そーなん", "だー", "．．．"]}, {"box": [474, 840, 547, 976], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["オレ．．．そんな", "子供っぽいこと", "しないよ。"]}], "img_path": "012.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [723, 104, 745, 169], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["ウソだ、"]}, {"box": [158, 121, 203, 198], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["ニヤ"]}, {"box": [561, 343, 610, 505], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["また", "からかってんだろ。"]}, {"box": [463, 316, 492, 478], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["書いてるのか！？"]}, {"box": [114, 321, 174, 505], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["書いたのかオレ！？", "忘れてるだけで。"]}, {"box": [347, 604, 425, 702], "vertical": true, "font_size": 27.0, "lines": ["か．．．か", "返して", "くれよぉ！！！"]}, {"box": [215, 619, 247, 675], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["ほい。"]}], "img_path": "013.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [739, 69, 789, 174], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["ち．．．ちが", "違うんだよ、"]}, {"box": [385, 65, 439, 258], "vertical": true, "font_size": 28.0, "lines": ["誰かが", "書いたんだよきっと！！"]}, {"box": [499, 459, 553, 575], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["何も書いて", "ないじゃん！！"]}, {"box": [331, 435, 411, 588], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["てか高木さん", "消しゴム持ってる", "じゃん！！！"]}, {"box": [106, 438, 144, 492], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["でっ"]}, {"box": [480, 883, 502, 986], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["うるせえよ。"]}, {"box": [235, 874, 287, 980], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["ス．．．", "スイマセン。"]}], "img_path": "014.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [713, 92, 742, 161], "vertical": true, "font_size": 29.0, "lines": ["ぷくく、"]}, {"box": [538, 91, 584, 234], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["あわてちゃって", "怒られちゃって。"]}, {"box": [398, 96, 472, 210], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["もー", "いいかげんに", "してよ。"]}, {"box": [28, 110, 74, 205], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["こっちの", "セリフだ！！"]}, {"box": [390, 296, 473, 452], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["先生ーー", "トイレ行ってきて", "いいですかー？"]}, {"box": [24, 328, 55, 380], "vertical": true, "font_size": 29.0, "lines": ["おう。"]}, {"box": [681, 577, 729, 683], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["くそっ．．．", "高木さんめ。"]}, {"box": [118, 563, 145, 685], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["今に見てろよ。"]}, {"box": [105, 892, 131, 989], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["そうだ！！"]}], "img_path": "015.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [678, 85, 780, 276], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["今のうちに", "高木さんの消しゴムに", "誰かの名前を", "書いといて．．．"]}, {"box": [387, 85, 460, 244], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["トイレから", "戻ってきたら", "からかってやろう"]}, {"box": [292, 71, 339, 186], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["さーて", "誰の名前を．．．"]}, {"box": [713, 576, 749, 633], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["な．．．"]}, {"box": [647, 854, 665, 899], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["．．．"]}, {"box": [485, 684, 569, 803], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["ＶｏＭ"]}, {"box": [172, 584, 229, 699], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["すでに", "書いてる！？"]}, {"box": [759, 860, 810, 976], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["見たら", "マズイか．．．！？"]}, {"box": [428, 861, 506, 978], "vertical": true, "font_size": 29.0, "lines": ["ひ．．．ひとも", "一文字", "くらいなら．．"]}], "img_path": "016.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [714, 105, 745, 151], "vertical": true, "font_size": 31.0, "lines": ["ろ！？"]}, {"box": [606, 125, 633, 169], "vertical": true, "font_size": 27.0, "lines": ["ろ！！！"]}, {"box": [503, 46, 548, 262], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["オレの名前じゃ"]}, {"box": [122, 48, 156, 203], "vertical": true, "font_size": 31.0, "lines": ["ないなぁ．．．"]}, {"box": [641, 295, 664, 409], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["てことは！？"]}, {"box": [116, 493, 257, 655], "vertical": true, "font_size": 31.0, "lines": ["いや．．．", "別に全然", "ショックとか", "じゃねーよ。"]}, {"box": [448, 819, 513, 955], "vertical": true, "font_size": 27.0, "lines": ["くそっ！！", "見てやる！！"]}, {"box": [192, 971, 250, 1058], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["スポン"]}, {"box": [56, 846, 124, 980], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["こうなりゃ", "全部！！"]}], "img_path": "017.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [534, 158, 653, 424], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["Ｃｒｒｅｔｓ"]}, {"box": [704, 865, 752, 966], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["や．．．"]}, {"box": [119, 839, 186, 1088], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["やられた！！！"]}], "img_path": "018.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [169, 61, 214, 163], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["ホントいい", "顔するわね"]}, {"box": [63, 67, 81, 112], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["．．．"]}, {"box": [694, 455, 741, 608], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["しかも思い通りの", "行動するし、"]}, {"box": [581, 453, 651, 592], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["これだから", "西片からかうの", "やめらんないわ。"]}, {"box": [678, 786, 702, 873], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["見てろよ、"]}, {"box": [508, 796, 612, 950], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["いつか絶対に", "からかって", "恥ずかしがらせて", "やる．．．．．！！"]}], "img_path": "019.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [682, 50, 741, 141], "vertical": true, "font_size": 30.0, "lines": ["期待", "してるわ。"]}, {"box": [579, 207, 641, 323], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["あっはっは"]}, {"box": [532, 50, 577, 183], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["あ！ムリだと", "思ってるだろ！！"]}, {"box": [398, 49, 418, 117], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["まーね。"]}, {"box": [120, 33, 167, 167], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["ホントだぞ！", "覚悟してろよ！！！"]}, {"box": [671, 424, 718, 510], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["ムリだと", "思うよー。"]}, {"box": [165, 426, 245, 570], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["大チャンスで", "二分の一を", "外すようじゃね。"]}, {"box": [754, 747, 807, 847], "vertical": true, "font_size": 30.0, "lines": ["は？", "二分の一？"]}, {"box": [663, 803, 698, 850], "vertical": true, "font_size": 30.0, "lines": ["何？"]}, {"box": [228, 745, 255, 849], "vertical": true, "font_size": 17.0, "lines": ["教えなーい。"]}], "img_path": "020.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [89, 87, 359, 176], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["プール"]}, {"box": [138, 967, 164, 1005], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["１"]}], "img_path": "021.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [564, 217, 656, 256], "vertical": false, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["あはは"]}, {"box": [299, 196, 513, 285], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["はははあは"]}, {"box": [275, 390, 351, 411], "vertical": false, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["はは"]}, {"box": [147, 404, 247, 424], "vertical": false, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["あははは"]}, {"box": [104, 454, 125, 513], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["はあ．．．"]}, {"box": [721, 670, 796, 774], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["いいなぁ．．．", "みんな", "楽しそうで。"]}, {"box": [165, 656, 189, 745], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["そーねー。"]}], "img_path": "022.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [642, 73, 742, 210], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["くそ．．．", "プール授業初日", "だっていうのに", "見学なんて．．．"]}, {"box": [302, 73, 353, 225], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["この手のケガさえ", "なきゃ．．．"]}, {"box": [657, 397, 729, 533], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["そういえば", "西片、その", "手のケガって．．．"]}, {"box": [313, 418, 370, 474], "vertical": true, "font_size": 30.0, "lines": ["え．．", "ああ。"]}, {"box": [200, 423, 246, 526], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["いろいろ．．．", "あって．．．ね。"]}, {"box": [543, 692, 645, 808], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["のらネコ", "なでようと", "したら噛まれ", "たんでしょ。"]}, {"box": [332, 699, 405, 908], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["え！？なんで", "知ってんの！？", "誰にも言ってないのに！"]}, {"box": [174, 694, 256, 869], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["あはは、正解なの！？", "テキトーに言った", "だけなのに！"]}, {"box": [56, 730, 80, 823], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["えぇえ！？"]}], "img_path": "023.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [697, 41, 720, 148], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["ドジだねー"]}, {"box": [381, 76, 401, 119], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["ぐ．．．"]}, {"box": [265, 51, 318, 163], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["高木さんは", "今日なんで、"]}, {"box": [100, 97, 135, 144], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["見．．．"]}, {"box": [568, 400, 596, 446], "vertical": true, "font_size": 28.0, "lines": ["が．．．"]}, {"box": [433, 393, 452, 438], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["く．．．"]}, {"box": [86, 395, 141, 525], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["さォさす"]}, {"box": [760, 925, 779, 1038], "vertical": true, "font_size": 16.0, "lines": ["そういえば．．．"]}, {"box": [590, 941, 670, 1085], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["プールを見学", "してる女子は", "だいたい生理だ、"]}, {"box": [342, 932, 397, 1055], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["生理は腹が", "痛いらしいぞ。"]}, {"box": [107, 933, 158, 1051], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["って、２組の", "高尾が！！"]}], "img_path": "024.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [714, 107, 742, 153], "vertical": true, "font_size": 28.0, "lines": ["ん？"]}, {"box": [576, 87, 621, 208], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["なんでもない"]}, {"box": [370, 94, 475, 269], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["見学の理由は", "聞かないでおこう：", "触れてはいけない", "気がする．．．"]}, {"box": [231, 108, 312, 207], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["なんで今日", "見学してる", "かって？"]}, {"box": [84, 51, 281, 71], "vertical": false, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["からかい上手の高い"]}, {"box": [100, 110, 150, 206], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["聞こえてん", "のかよ！！"]}, {"box": [628, 468, 739, 690], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["じゃあ、私", "西片のケガのこと", "当てたんだから、"]}, {"box": [144, 502, 178, 679], "vertical": true, "font_size": 31.0, "lines": ["当ててみてよ。"]}], "img_path": "025.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [698, 87, 746, 186], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["た．．．", "体調不良？"]}, {"box": [376, 77, 451, 194], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["そんな", "あいまいなの", "ダメだよ。"]}, {"box": [290, 111, 328, 179], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["いや．．．"]}, {"box": [161, 113, 237, 213], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["別にいいよ", "知りたく", "ないし．．．"]}, {"box": [384, 507, 455, 670], "vertical": true, "font_size": 30.0, "lines": ["じゃあ私の", "勝ちでいい？"]}, {"box": [583, 920, 730, 1090], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["わかったよ！！", "当てれば", "いいんだろ！！"]}, {"box": [223, 918, 248, 1004], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["一発でね。"]}, {"box": [120, 966, 167, 1120], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["まぁ当たらないと", "思うけど。"]}], "img_path": "026.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [653, 67, 742, 254], "vertical": true, "font_size": 29.0, "lines": ["高木さんめ．．．オレが", "生理って言えないと", "思っての自信か？"]}, {"box": [454, 73, 526, 171], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["だとしたら", "オレを甘く", "見すぎ．．．"]}, {"box": [349, 98, 402, 270], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["いや待て！", "高木さんのことだ！"]}, {"box": [108, 78, 181, 212], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["これは", "トラップの", "可能性もある！！"]}, {"box": [494, 532, 522, 616], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["失礼な奴。"]}, {"box": [110, 549, 162, 646], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["十分に", "ありえる！！"]}, {"box": [633, 527, 738, 679], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["オレが勇気を", "ふりしぼって", "「生理」と", "答えたところで．．"]}, {"box": [660, 796, 738, 950], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["いや、しかし", "そこまで読んでの", "．．．"]}, {"box": [523, 810, 596, 925], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["クソ、わけが", "わからなく", "なってきた．．"]}, {"box": [178, 808, 254, 906], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["そうだ．．．", "他の可能性", "は．．．！"]}], "img_path": "027.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [693, 108, 746, 225], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["高木さんに", "ケガとかは．．"]}, {"box": [113, 82, 158, 174], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["ないみたい", "だな．．．"]}, {"box": [656, 550, 701, 645], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["だとしたら", "やはり．．．"]}, {"box": [108, 257, 187, 432], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["運動できないほど", "体調が悪いわけでも", "なさそうだ"]}, {"box": [165, 553, 190, 630], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["いや．．．"]}], "img_path": "028.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [682, 46, 736, 202], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["いいなぁ、みんな", "楽しそうで．．"]}, {"box": [319, 63, 452, 217], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["オレは暑いな", "こんなに頭を", "フル回転させて", "高木さんと戦って", "いるのに．．．"]}, {"box": [666, 426, 746, 526], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["西片", "ちゃんと", "考えてる？"]}, {"box": [358, 427, 488, 546], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["なんか", "さっきから", "泳いでる女子", "ばっかり", "見てない？"]}, {"box": [105, 426, 164, 566], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["み．．．", "見てないよ！！"]}, {"box": [713, 738, 733, 858], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["ホントかなー、"]}, {"box": [364, 767, 442, 910], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["男子ってすぐに", "女子の胸ばっか", "見るって言うし。"]}, {"box": [236, 724, 287, 860], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["だから", "見てないって．．．"]}, {"box": [123, 735, 156, 819], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["はっ！！！"]}], "img_path": "029.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [418, 100, 470, 261], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["高木さんは．．．", "言っちゃあ悪いが、"]}, {"box": [125, 123, 173, 220], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["あまり", "胸がない："]}, {"box": [667, 555, 776, 733], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["胸の小さい女子って、", "そのコトを", "気にしてる場合が", "多いらしいぜ。"]}, {"box": [132, 587, 196, 724], "vertical": true, "font_size": 28.0, "lines": ["って、３組の", "木村が．．．！！"]}, {"box": [715, 849, 772, 973], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["まさか", "高木さんは、"]}, {"box": [162, 850, 292, 1035], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["自分の胸が", "コンプレックスで", "プールを見学", "しているのか！？"]}], "img_path": "030.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [631, 139, 733, 253], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["って．．．", "言えるワケ", "ないだろ", "そんなコト！！！"]}, {"box": [83, 49, 370, 73], "vertical": false, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["からかい上手の高ホさんの"]}, {"box": [125, 131, 177, 268], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["失礼すぎるにも", "程があるよ！！"]}, {"box": [682, 454, 756, 597], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["結局．．．こた", "答えられるのは", "生理だけなのか．．．"]}, {"box": [438, 482, 488, 562], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["しかし", "生理も．．．"]}, {"box": [353, 457, 401, 576], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["まだ", "考えてんの？"]}, {"box": [101, 483, 147, 569], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["そろそろ", "答えてよ。"]}, {"box": [644, 728, 746, 901], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["いや、教科書に", "のってることは", "恥ずかしいコトじゃ", "ないんだ．．．！"]}, {"box": [533, 727, 581, 880], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["そうさ、堂々と", "言えばいいのさ！！"]}, {"box": [100, 715, 139, 862], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["ズバリ！！"]}], "img_path": "031.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [772, 76, 802, 135], "vertical": true, "font_size": 15.0, "lines": ["せいり．．．", "だから．．．？"]}, {"box": [308, 485, 333, 564], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["はずれ。"]}, {"box": [660, 738, 741, 835], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["女の子に", "なんてコト", "言うのよ。"]}, {"box": [260, 711, 307, 823], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["いや．．．だって", "これは．．．！！"]}, {"box": [360, 872, 390, 901], "vertical": false, "font_size": 29.0, "lines": ["！？"]}, {"box": [111, 788, 132, 867], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["プクク．．．"]}], "img_path": "032.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [685, 116, 727, 302], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["「あははは。"]}, {"box": [124, 63, 196, 284], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["顔、真っ赤っかに", "なってるよ！"]}, {"box": [51, 148, 84, 283], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["あははは。"]}, {"box": [721, 483, 744, 598], "vertical": true, "font_size": 17.0, "lines": ["ううう．．．"]}, {"box": [222, 475, 303, 629], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["正解は．．．胸の", "コンプレックスの", "方だったのか．．．？"]}, {"box": [709, 794, 731, 862], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["よっと。"]}, {"box": [71, 791, 93, 882], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["はあっ！？"]}], "img_path": "033.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [380, 148, 401, 232], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["ちなみに、"]}, {"box": [214, 114, 267, 267], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["胸が小さいのが", "恥ずかしいから．．．"]}, {"box": [693, 801, 740, 922], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["ってのも", "ハズレだから。"]}, {"box": [487, 796, 513, 860], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["え．．．？"]}, {"box": [377, 803, 424, 881], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["じゃあ．．．", "なんで．．．"]}, {"box": [196, 782, 285, 922], "vertical": true, "font_size": 29.0, "lines": ["先生ー", "やっぱり泳いで", "いいですかー？"]}, {"box": [106, 798, 126, 882], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["オッケー"]}], "img_path": "034.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [317, 72, 411, 270], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["じゃ、いい顔", "見れたし", "泳いでこよっかな。"]}, {"box": [702, 528, 726, 667], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["ま、まさか！"]}, {"box": [315, 529, 404, 689], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["オレをからかう", "ためだけに", "見学を！？"]}, {"box": [358, 983, 377, 1030], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["．．．"]}], "img_path": "035.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [426, 75, 490, 246], "vertical": true, "font_size": 30.0, "lines": ["手治ったら", "一緒に泳ごーね。"]}, {"box": [345, 331, 371, 363], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["わ、"]}, {"box": [236, 318, 319, 360], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["ドライ"]}, {"box": [130, 337, 152, 422], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["つめたっ。"]}, {"box": [672, 642, 745, 720], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["．．．くそ．．．", "だまされ", "ないぞ．．．"]}, {"box": [140, 628, 223, 801], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["一緒に泳いでる時に", "またオレのこと", "からかう気なんだ。"]}, {"box": [698, 882, 725, 1004], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["そういう人だ、"]}, {"box": [174, 901, 204, 1005], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["高木さんは。"]}], "img_path": "036.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [302, 105, 569, 244], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["がお", "顔", "変"]}], "img_path": "037.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [663, 145, 728, 282], "vertical": true, "font_size": 29.0, "lines": ["だから", "違うって！！"]}, {"box": [146, 116, 215, 387], "vertical": true, "font_size": 30.0, "lines": ["おねしょは、とっくに", "卒業してるっての！！"]}, {"box": [179, 535, 198, 650], "vertical": true, "font_size": 16.0, "lines": ["くつくっく．．．"]}, {"box": [618, 651, 694, 748], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["おねしょが", "どうした", "西片ー"]}, {"box": [434, 551, 508, 653], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["い、いえ", "なんでも．．．", "ありません"]}, {"box": [485, 843, 504, 945], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["バカだねー、"]}, {"box": [270, 833, 319, 956], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["ムキに", "なっちゃって。"]}, {"box": [207, 837, 224, 877], "vertical": true, "font_size": 17.0, "lines": ["ぐ．．．"]}], "img_path": "038.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [549, 70, 592, 258], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["高木さんめ！！"]}, {"box": [140, 82, 476, 276], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["わ"]}, {"box": [85, 51, 357, 71], "vertical": false, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["からかいと手の高ホさんは"]}, {"box": [376, 348, 477, 464], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["どうすれば", "高木さんに", "勝てるんだ．．．", "どうすれば"]}, {"box": [681, 773, 728, 888], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["どうすれば", "いいと思う？"]}, {"box": [482, 767, 507, 830], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["オレ．．．"]}, {"box": [343, 771, 423, 915], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["お、西片", "なんだ鏡なんて", "見つめて。"]}, {"box": [85, 774, 159, 841], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["中井君．．．"]}], "img_path": "039.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [674, 123, 753, 237], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["キメ顔の", "練習でも", "してたのか？"]}, {"box": [361, 108, 383, 175], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["まさか。"]}, {"box": [113, 113, 162, 194], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["じゃあ", "変顔か？"]}, {"box": [613, 264, 671, 358], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["ははは"]}, {"box": [745, 772, 795, 833], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["なる", "ほど．．．"]}, {"box": [592, 769, 617, 830], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["よし．．"]}, {"box": [432, 766, 530, 903], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["ところでさ、", "西片ってやけに", "高木さんと", "仲いいよな。"]}, {"box": [288, 753, 337, 829], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["こ．．．", "こうか？"]}, {"box": [145, 783, 215, 853], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["？"]}], "img_path": "040.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [676, 82, 754, 216], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["西片って", "もしかして", "高木さんのこと"]}, {"box": [571, 79, 641, 217], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["ハハッ！！", "バハハハ！"]}, {"box": [384, 113, 456, 228], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["おもしろい！！", "これは．．．", "いけるぞっ！！"]}, {"box": [260, 55, 281, 131], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["フフフ．．．"]}, {"box": [125, 82, 226, 216], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["フ．．．", "ごまかそうと", "するってことは", "そうなんだな．．．"]}, {"box": [589, 459, 744, 653], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["西片！", "お前ズバリ", "高木さんのこと", "好．．．．．"]}, {"box": [123, 491, 165, 590], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["ブフー"]}, {"box": [77, 595, 112, 636], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["！！！"]}, {"box": [667, 909, 741, 1026], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["なんだよ", "西片", "その顔――！！"]}, {"box": [221, 902, 292, 1035], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["オレに．．．", "こんな才能が", "あったなんて．．"]}], "img_path": "041.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [668, 310, 742, 427], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["よーし、", "じゃあ授業", "始めるぞー"]}, {"box": [358, 348, 410, 435], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["３６ページ", "開いてー。"]}, {"box": [242, 345, 275, 417], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["いいぞ、"]}, {"box": [125, 332, 200, 469], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["うまい具合に", "怒ると一番怖い", "田辺先生だ。"]}, {"box": [625, 714, 754, 901], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["オレの変顔で", "爆笑して", "たっぷり怒られる", "高木さん。"]}], "img_path": "042.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [679, 50, 709, 111], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["１０分後"]}, {"box": [509, 128, 589, 246], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["ああ、早く", "高木さんを", "笑わせたい．．．"]}, {"box": [359, 43, 465, 215], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["高木さんがオレを", "からかおうと", "声をかけてくるまで", "ガマンするんだ"]}, {"box": [99, 50, 201, 242], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["人をからかおうと", "している時は、自分が", "からかわれるなんて", "警戒心は薄くなる。"]}, {"box": [511, 350, 563, 471], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["いや．．．", "ガマンだオレ"]}, {"box": [116, 296, 177, 400], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["そこを叩くっ！！"]}, {"box": [112, 292, 176, 407], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["そこを", "叩くっ！！"]}, {"box": [629, 536, 728, 680], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["さぁ、くるがいい", "高木さん、", "オレは隙", "だらけだよ！！"]}, {"box": [490, 853, 544, 907], "vertical": true, "font_size": 29.0, "lines": ["ねえ", "西片。"]}, {"box": [392, 835, 453, 1038], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["きたっ！！"]}], "img_path": "043.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [694, 100, 741, 185], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["なんだい", "高木さん。"]}, {"box": [354, 99, 395, 282], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["くらえっ！！"]}, {"box": [107, 984, 175, 1068], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["あ．．．", "あれ！？"]}], "img_path": "044.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [408, 58, 456, 173], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["ぶっ！！！"]}, {"box": [260, 83, 351, 233], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["あはは", "ははは："]}, {"box": [100, 69, 121, 146], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["おーい．．．"]}, {"box": [421, 483, 510, 667], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["うるせぇぞ", "西片ァ！！"]}, {"box": [187, 500, 238, 618], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["ス．．．", "スイマセン！！"]}, {"box": [188, 861, 213, 923], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["くそ．．．"]}, {"box": [541, 878, 593, 963], "vertical": true, "font_size": 28.0, "lines": ["こ．．．こえ", "怖えー"]}, {"box": [417, 874, 440, 949], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["ぷくくっ"]}], "img_path": "045.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [653, 112, 732, 229], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["何をしようと", "してるのかと", "思ったら．．．"]}, {"box": [400, 123, 447, 218], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["つまんない", "なー"]}, {"box": [323, 116, 347, 176], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["な．．．．．"]}, {"box": [99, 112, 178, 247], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["変顔だったら", "もっとまゆ毛を", "こうしてさー。"]}, {"box": [654, 596, 711, 712], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["で、両方の", "ほっぺたを．．．"]}, {"box": [549, 646, 569, 709], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["．．．．．．"]}, {"box": [276, 639, 301, 701], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["こう？"]}, {"box": [454, 876, 472, 910], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["．．．"]}, {"box": [130, 662, 183, 718], "vertical": true, "font_size": 28.0, "lines": ["そう", "そう。"]}, {"box": [111, 844, 162, 952], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["それで", "もっとさー。"]}, {"box": [681, 867, 728, 950], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["うんうん", "いい感じ、"]}, {"box": [533, 919, 579, 1033], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["さっきよりは", "いいよ。"]}, {"box": [429, 853, 446, 952], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["なんだろう。"]}], "img_path": "046.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [563, 58, 718, 244], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["笑わせようと", "してる相手に", "どうやったら", "笑えるかを", "指導されるって．．．"]}, {"box": [160, 58, 253, 175], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["なんか", "屈辱．．．"]}, {"box": [567, 310, 641, 445], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["そのまま", "もっとギュッて", "してさー、"]}, {"box": [460, 532, 485, 594], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["こう？"]}, {"box": [320, 530, 370, 610], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["うん！", "いいよ！"]}, {"box": [190, 355, 247, 454], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["目力もっと", "入れて。"]}, {"box": [53, 527, 105, 644], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["スゴく", "よくなった！"]}, {"box": [627, 528, 728, 683], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["いや、いいさ！", "高木さんが笑って", "先生に怒られさえ", "すればオレは！！"]}, {"box": [685, 875, 716, 928], "vertical": true, "font_size": 27.0, "lines": ["いや、"]}, {"box": [590, 876, 641, 964], "vertical": true, "font_size": 27.0, "lines": ["じゃあ", "笑ってよ。"]}, {"box": [451, 868, 504, 1001], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["それで横顔なら", "大爆笑だよ。"]}, {"box": [89, 864, 234, 1052], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["よし！", "くらえ", "高木さん！！"]}], "img_path": "047.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [695, 676, 726, 740], "vertical": true, "font_size": 31.0, "lines": ["ぶっ．．．"]}, {"box": [557, 956, 654, 1176], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["何してんだ", "西片ァアア！！"]}, {"box": [186, 980, 251, 1144], "vertical": true, "font_size": 28.0, "lines": ["スイマセン！", "スイマセン！"]}], "img_path": "048.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [701, 92, 719, 187], "vertical": true, "font_size": 17.0, "lines": ["まったく．．．"]}, {"box": [372, 62, 422, 167], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["ホント", "スイマセン。"]}, {"box": [233, 18, 254, 116], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["ぷっくく．．．"]}, {"box": [154, 476, 171, 511], "vertical": true, "font_size": 17.0, "lines": ["！"]}, {"box": [723, 591, 741, 653], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["もー"]}, {"box": [665, 692, 736, 846], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["あははは"]}, {"box": [440, 585, 490, 664], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["おなか", "いたい．．．"]}, {"box": [111, 598, 182, 714], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["たしかに", "爆笑はしてる", "けどさあ．．．"]}, {"box": [676, 896, 725, 1018], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["．．．", "またやられた。"]}], "img_path": "049.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [700, 179, 756, 233], "vertical": true, "font_size": 29.0, "lines": ["ねえ、にしかた", "西片"]}, {"box": [362, 253, 382, 317], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["．．．．．．？"]}, {"box": [136, 251, 155, 315], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["．．．．．．"]}, {"box": [637, 532, 736, 700], "vertical": true, "font_size": 30.0, "lines": ["次に田辺先生を", "怒らせたら", "本当にマズイ．．．"]}, {"box": [475, 864, 495, 910], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["．．．"]}, {"box": [89, 533, 247, 720], "vertical": true, "font_size": 28.0, "lines": ["とにかく", "この授業の間は", "高木さんに", "関わらないように", "しないと．．．"]}], "img_path": "050.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [76, 584, 171, 666], "vertical": true, "font_size": 31.0, "lines": ["やっと", "こっち", "向いた。"]}], "img_path": "051.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [503, 94, 576, 210], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["にーらめっこ", "しーましょ", "あーっぷっ．．．"]}, {"box": [215, 73, 243, 103], "vertical": true, "font_size": 28.0, "lines": ["ぷ"]}, {"box": [336, 410, 366, 455], "vertical": true, "font_size": 30.0, "lines": ["へ？"]}, {"box": [695, 638, 741, 723], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["ぶ．．．"]}, {"box": [558, 850, 701, 1039], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["ハハハ！", "何その顔！", "高木さん！！"]}, {"box": [346, 862, 441, 1051], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["西片ァアア", "コラァア！！"]}, {"box": [149, 867, 229, 1027], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["高木さんに", "ドキドキした時は", "ロクなコトがない。"]}], "img_path": "052.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [233, 33, 511, 167], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["各", "筋トレ"]}], "img_path": "053.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [577, 202, 652, 301], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["あはは。", "じゃあまた", "明日ねー。"]}, {"box": [603, 837, 631, 902], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["くっ．．．"]}, {"box": [304, 844, 358, 960], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["今に見ていろ", "高木さんめ．．．"]}], "img_path": "054.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [565, 63, 631, 250], "vertical": true, "font_size": 30.0, "lines": ["オレには今日、", "作戦があるのさ！！"]}, {"box": [324, 119, 431, 272], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["帰り道の２回も", "合わせて．．．", "今日は１５回も", "からかわれた．．．"]}, {"box": [85, 51, 353, 71], "vertical": false, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["からかいと手の高ホさんは"]}, {"box": [649, 537, 705, 636], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["１５回Ｘ１０で", "１５０回か．．．"]}, {"box": [343, 393, 398, 438], "vertical": false, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["バヤッ"]}, {"box": [324, 537, 341, 600], "vertical": true, "font_size": 17.0, "lines": ["．．．．．．？"]}, {"box": [99, 530, 154, 701], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["１５０回：初回にしては", "ハードな気が．．．"]}, {"box": [626, 895, 687, 1010], "vertical": true, "font_size": 28.0, "lines": ["いや！", "やるんだ！！"]}, {"box": [90, 902, 179, 1040], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["それくらい", "じゃなきゃ", "ダメなんだ！！"]}], "img_path": "055.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [603, 39, 755, 255], "vertical": true, "font_size": 30.0, "lines": ["その日高木さんに", "からかわれた", "回数の十倍の", "回数の．．．"]}, {"box": [147, 37, 206, 251], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["腕立て．．．！！"]}, {"box": [682, 656, 702, 734], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["じゅう．．．"]}, {"box": [517, 643, 539, 736], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["はちぃ！！"]}, {"box": [364, 613, 440, 719], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["思ったより", "メチャクチャ", "キツイで．．．"]}, {"box": [299, 610, 317, 644], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["ハア"]}, {"box": [84, 611, 140, 719], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["少し回数を", "減らすか．．．？"]}, {"box": [103, 868, 168, 1004], "vertical": true, "font_size": 29.0, "lines": ["いや！！", "ダメだッ！！！"]}], "img_path": "056.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [596, 90, 709, 365], "vertical": true, "font_size": 30.0, "lines": ["これは普段からかわれ", "すぎている自分への：", "罰なのだ。"]}, {"box": [454, 53, 505, 204], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["この苦しみを", "噛みしめながら．．．"]}, {"box": [72, 73, 147, 208], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["次こそはという", "意識を高める", "のだ．．．"]}, {"box": [73, 276, 145, 408], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["この罰の目的は", "そこにあるの", "だから．．．！！"]}, {"box": [617, 532, 737, 694], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["がんばれオレ！", "こんな苦しみを", "味わいたく", "なければ．．．"]}, {"box": [637, 818, 674, 971], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["見てろよ！！"]}, {"box": [103, 527, 228, 711], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["明日からはもっと", "からかわれない", "ように気を", "つけるんだ！"]}, {"box": [492, 1027, 513, 1100], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["ひゃく．．．"]}, {"box": [444, 1078, 460, 1170], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["ごじゅう．．．"]}, {"box": [187, 867, 233, 1026], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["高木さん！！"]}], "img_path": "057.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [114, 330, 134, 410], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["くう．．．"]}, {"box": [256, 576, 283, 605], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["え、"]}, {"box": [748, 587, 798, 664], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["おはよー", "．．．？"]}, {"box": [646, 624, 699, 714], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["腕どうか", "したの？"]}, {"box": [549, 569, 575, 631], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["ケガ？"]}, {"box": [134, 578, 209, 684], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["ああ、いや", "別にただの", "筋肉痛だよ。"]}, {"box": [733, 925, 760, 1002], "vertical": true, "font_size": 27.0, "lines": ["へえー"]}], "img_path": "058.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [597, 60, 630, 118], "vertical": true, "font_size": 31.0, "lines": ["えい。"]}, {"box": [460, 50, 490, 200], "vertical": true, "font_size": 28.0, "lines": ["うわぁああ"]}, {"box": [235, 62, 309, 196], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["やめてよ", "ホントに", "痛いんだから！！"]}, {"box": [667, 496, 721, 629], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["今のは１回に", "数えるのか．．．？"]}, {"box": [182, 331, 216, 386], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["ケラ"]}, {"box": [117, 503, 223, 677], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["．．．ここは自分に", "厳しくいくべきだ、", "１回としてカウント", "しておこう．．．"]}, {"box": [613, 769, 638, 833], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["とう！"]}, {"box": [494, 768, 542, 867], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["ヒッ！！！"]}, {"box": [311, 782, 438, 907], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["あはは", "だまされたー。", "よっぽど", "ひどいんだね", "筋肉痛。"]}, {"box": [115, 779, 190, 933], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["くっ．．．", "これは確実に", "からかわれたな．．．"]}], "img_path": "059.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [451, 78, 527, 213], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["で、", "なんでいきなり", "筋肉痛なの？"]}, {"box": [331, 105, 384, 264], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["いや、昨日から", "筋トレを始めてね。"]}, {"box": [687, 516, 741, 687], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["へぇー、三日坊主に", "ならないといいね。"]}, {"box": [295, 825, 344, 908], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["見ていろ", "高木さん、"]}, {"box": [105, 525, 160, 697], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["フッ．．．言っているが", "いい、高木さんめ。"]}, {"box": [106, 829, 234, 970], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["オレは腕立てを", "したくないから、", "からかわれない", "ように全力で", "がんばるぞ．．．！！"]}, {"box": [654, 832, 732, 986], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["この筋トレという", "苦行から解放", "される時．．．"]}, {"box": [399, 832, 497, 982], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["それすなわち", "オレが高木さんに", "からかわれなく", "なった証なのだ。"]}], "img_path": "060.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [574, 87, 628, 260], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["本日高木さんに", "からかわれた回数：："]}, {"box": [115, 126, 167, 212], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["２３回。"]}, {"box": [616, 600, 736, 833], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["えええ！？", "なんでだ！！", "昨日よりも多く", "なってるじゃないか？"]}, {"box": [114, 613, 151, 795], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["なんでだ！？"]}, {"box": [644, 962, 719, 1085], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["くそっ．．．", "もうイヤだ", "筋トレなんて。"]}, {"box": [503, 1012, 537, 1060], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["１０６．．．"]}, {"box": [372, 1046, 400, 1089], "vertical": true, "font_size": 28.0, "lines": ["１０７．"]}, {"box": [128, 944, 205, 1133], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["明日こそは", "からかわれないように", "気をつけねば．．．"]}], "img_path": "061.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [653, 101, 683, 162], "vertical": true, "font_size": 27.0, "lines": ["３日後"]}, {"box": [268, 325, 322, 440], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["本日からかわ", "れた回数．．．"]}, {"box": [219, 349, 249, 405], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["５４回。"]}, {"box": [110, 305, 158, 486], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["なぜだっ！！日に日に", "増えてるぞ！！"]}, {"box": [643, 755, 746, 890], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["すごく", "警戒してるって", "いうのに．．．", "なぜだ．．．"]}, {"box": [538, 753, 586, 889], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["それ自体がきうか", "逆効果なのか！？"]}, {"box": [412, 767, 460, 863], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["そういえば", "西片："]}, {"box": [292, 771, 350, 873], "vertical": true, "font_size": 30.0, "lines": ["筋トレ", "続いてる？"]}], "img_path": "062.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [523, 116, 570, 210], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["あぁ．．．うん", "一応ね．．．"]}, {"box": [390, 104, 466, 226], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["へぇー、", "三日坊主じゃ", "なかったねー。"]}, {"box": [83, 51, 370, 71], "vertical": false, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["からかいと手の高ホさんは"]}, {"box": [107, 110, 130, 262], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["おかげさまで．．．！！"]}, {"box": [687, 502, 733, 598], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["あ、でもさ", "知ってる？"]}, {"box": [147, 505, 217, 567], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["え？何？"]}, {"box": [230, 651, 366, 861], "vertical": true, "font_size": 27.0, "lines": ["成長期に", "筋トレしすぎると", "身長止まっちゃう", "って言われてるの。"]}], "img_path": "063.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [716, 701, 739, 816], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["ぇえええ！？"]}, {"box": [508, 680, 580, 870], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["そういえば．．．", "どこかでそんなコトを", "聞いた覚えが．．．"]}, {"box": [298, 693, 449, 866], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["それはマズイ．．．", "高木さんの方が", "身長が高くなって", "しまったら、今まで", "以上にからかわれて", "しまうじゃないか。"]}, {"box": [128, 692, 194, 875], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["どうしよう：", "どうしよう．．．"]}], "img_path": "064.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [674, 55, 748, 205], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["ここ数日で", "かなり筋トレ", "しちゃったそ．．．！！"]}, {"box": [585, 58, 634, 195], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["今からやめても", "遅いか．．．！？"]}, {"box": [417, 58, 488, 188], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["まぁアレって", "まったくのデマ", "らしいけどね。"]}, {"box": [602, 548, 729, 699], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["デマなの！？", "なんで言わなくて", "いいことを", "言うのさ", "高木さん！！！"]}, {"box": [339, 540, 438, 696], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["むしろ適度な", "筋トレは", "成長ホルモンが", "活発になるとかで、"]}, {"box": [373, 847, 393, 926], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["ぐぬぬ．．．"]}, {"box": [237, 548, 306, 673], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["身長伸びやすく", "なったりする", "らしいよ。"]}, {"box": [79, 645, 128, 741], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["ムシしない", "でよ！！"]}, {"box": [663, 848, 742, 972], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["いやー、", "その反応が", "見たくてさぁ。"]}, {"box": [205, 844, 304, 980], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["まぁ、そういう", "コトだから", "安心して筋トレ", "続けなよ。"]}], "img_path": "065.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [726, 84, 765, 255], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["いいと思うよ、"]}, {"box": [185, 413, 286, 642], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["ちょっとだけど", "なんかたくましく", "なった気がするし。"]}, {"box": [646, 905, 668, 1002], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["あ、そう．．．"]}], "img_path": "066.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [317, 118, 364, 242], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["どしたの？", "黙っちゃって。"]}, {"box": [84, 51, 354, 71], "vertical": false, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["からかいと手の高ホさんは"]}, {"box": [106, 472, 128, 548], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["いや．．．"]}, {"box": [688, 687, 733, 785], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["もしかして", "テレてる？"]}, {"box": [472, 706, 520, 800], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["テ．．．テレて", "なんか．．．"]}, {"box": [386, 706, 404, 785], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["．．．"]}, {"box": [200, 682, 276, 768], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["あはは", "テレてる", "テレてる。"]}, {"box": [473, 971, 502, 1057], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["顔赤いよ。"]}], "img_path": "067.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [685, 103, 731, 274], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["もー、なんなんだよ", "ぃつもいつもー。"]}, {"box": [486, 118, 566, 214], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["反応おもし", "ろいから", "だってば。"]}, {"box": [383, 70, 407, 137], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["それに、"]}, {"box": [105, 276, 178, 430], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["たくましくなった", "気がするってのは", "本当だよ。"]}, {"box": [636, 578, 709, 749], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["ちょっと", "カッコ良く", "なったんじゃない？"]}, {"box": [620, 862, 670, 1023], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["あはは", "もっと赤くなった。"]}, {"box": [436, 892, 488, 1025], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["違うよ！", "暑いからだよ！"]}, {"box": [153, 901, 281, 1092], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["とりあえず", "高木さんにからかわれ", "なくなっても", "筋トレは続けようと", "思った。"]}], "img_path": "068.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [], "img_path": "069.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [369, 1078, 763, 1113], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["からかい上手の高木さん"]}], "img_path": "070.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [229, 63, 533, 193], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["ぅ", "空き缶", "かん"]}, {"box": [285, 803, 335, 921], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["でもぁした", "明日こそは．．．"]}, {"box": [124, 851, 153, 921], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["西片ー。"]}, {"box": [401, 823, 484, 997], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["今日も一日", "さんざん高木さんに", "からかわれたなぁ．．．"]}], "img_path": "071.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [750, 88, 777, 205], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["今日は一人？"]}, {"box": [385, 113, 466, 201], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["途中まで", "一緒に", "帰ろーよ。"]}, {"box": [221, 108, 295, 232], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["え、でも", "高木さん", "チャリじゃん。"]}, {"box": [119, 150, 147, 235], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["押すもん。"]}, {"box": [649, 905, 748, 1020], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["そのジュース", "最近出た", "やつだよね、", "おいしい？"]}], "img_path": "072.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [709, 49, 735, 170], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["おいしいよ、"]}, {"box": [301, 75, 332, 189], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["一口飲む？"]}, {"box": [209, 127, 230, 202], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["いいの？"]}, {"box": [107, 133, 139, 191], "vertical": true, "font_size": 28.0, "lines": ["うん。"]}, {"box": [660, 471, 711, 556], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["じゃあ", "遠慮なく。"]}, {"box": [312, 478, 343, 514], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["あ、"]}, {"box": [227, 466, 275, 600], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["別にいいけど", "これってさぁ．．．"]}, {"box": [493, 769, 562, 900], "vertical": true, "font_size": 27.0, "lines": ["間接キス．．．", "だよね。"]}, {"box": [206, 757, 278, 855], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["フフフ．．．！", "どうだ", "高木さん！"]}, {"box": [94, 764, 144, 861], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["恥ずかしい", "だろう！？"]}, {"box": [235, 1026, 290, 1105], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["恥ずかし", "がれっ！！"]}], "img_path": "073.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [244, 56, 272, 106], "vertical": true, "font_size": 28.0, "lines": ["な．．．"]}, {"box": [693, 512, 750, 604], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["なんだと", "．．．！？"]}, {"box": [125, 515, 230, 668], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["まったく恥ずかし", "がらない．．．！？", "どうなってんの", "この人．．．．．．！？"]}, {"box": [693, 752, 723, 806], "vertical": true, "font_size": 30.0, "lines": ["ほい、"]}, {"box": [527, 747, 574, 851], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["ありがと", "おいしいね。"]}, {"box": [112, 970, 167, 1087], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["飲まないの？", "西片。"]}], "img_path": "074.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [611, 107, 740, 264], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["くそ．．．", "ここで少しでも", "恥ずかしがったら", "高木さんの", "思うつぼだ．．．"]}, {"box": [387, 105, 465, 203], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["いや．．．", "飲むよっ", "ぜんぜん．．．"]}, {"box": [261, 104, 334, 256], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["なんでもない．．", "こんなのなんでも", "ないさ．．．"]}, {"box": [86, 51, 351, 71], "vertical": false, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["からかいと手の高ホさん"]}, {"box": [339, 517, 411, 622], "vertical": true, "font_size": 30.0, "lines": ["間接キス", "だね。"]}, {"box": [435, 926, 462, 1021], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["あぁっ！！"]}, {"box": [72, 912, 119, 1016], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["あはは", "何してんの。"]}], "img_path": "075.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [378, 96, 407, 166], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["くそっ。"]}, {"box": [698, 912, 726, 967], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["わお。"]}], "img_path": "076.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [702, 85, 749, 208], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["へぇ、よく", "入ったね西片。"]}, {"box": [483, 210, 556, 359], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["つい投げちゃった", "けど．．．", "まさか入るなんて、"]}], "img_path": "077.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [668, 123, 739, 242], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["オレに．．．", "こんな才能が", "あったなんて"]}, {"box": [481, 107, 558, 205], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["よーし", "私もやって", "みよー。"]}, {"box": [270, 513, 297, 564], "vertical": true, "font_size": 27.0, "lines": ["むむ。"]}, {"box": [106, 512, 130, 617], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["フッフップ。"]}, {"box": [675, 917, 743, 1122], "vertical": true, "font_size": 28.0, "lines": ["ほっはっはー", "どこ狙ってんの。"]}, {"box": [117, 892, 220, 1057], "vertical": true, "font_size": 29.0, "lines": ["ぜんっぜん", "届いてないよ", "高木さん！！！"]}], "img_path": "078.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [547, 62, 630, 161], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["何よ！", "じゃあ勝負", "する！？"]}, {"box": [416, 48, 493, 192], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["ハハハ！勝負？", "別にいいよ", "負けないしオレ。"]}, {"box": [281, 21, 359, 196], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["じゃあ１回ずつ", "投げて、先に入れた", "方が勝ちね。"]}, {"box": [117, 55, 165, 196], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["フフ．．．", "取り乱している。"]}, {"box": [670, 500, 745, 636], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["高木さんが", "冷静さを", "失っている．．．！"]}, {"box": [591, 501, 613, 635], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["オレのせいで！！"]}, {"box": [119, 495, 181, 645], "vertical": true, "font_size": 27.0, "lines": ["なんて", "いい気分だ！！"]}, {"box": [635, 907, 739, 1061], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["もし高木さんが", "勝ったらなんでも", "言うコト聞いて", "あげるよ。"]}, {"box": [113, 926, 166, 1041], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["言ってくれる", "わね！"]}], "img_path": "079.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [644, 108, 746, 261], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["聞いたからね、", "私が勝ったら", "なんでも言うこと", "聞くのね？"]}, {"box": [456, 118, 477, 220], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["あーいいよ、"]}, {"box": [238, 87, 313, 210], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["まぁオレが", "負けるわけ", "ないけどねー。"]}], "img_path": "080.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [623, 35, 711, 213], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["は！？"]}, {"box": [695, 262, 720, 350], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["ぷくくく。"]}, {"box": [697, 489, 745, 641], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["あははは", "バカみたいな顔！"]}, {"box": [381, 460, 464, 615], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["本気で私が", "この程度の距離", "外すと思ったの！？"]}, {"box": [238, 481, 311, 563], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["ほらほら", "さっさと", "投げなよ、"]}, {"box": [55, 772, 133, 862], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["外したら", "私の勝ち", "だからね。"]}, {"box": [647, 951, 700, 1039], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["や．．．", "やられた。"]}, {"box": [151, 949, 169, 1063], "vertical": true, "font_size": 16.0, "lines": ["またしても．．"]}], "img_path": "081.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [701, 595, 721, 671], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["いける．．．"]}, {"box": [178, 602, 234, 684], "vertical": true, "font_size": 29.0, "lines": ["絶対にはい", "入る．．．！！！"]}, {"box": [100, 891, 154, 962], "vertical": true, "font_size": 28.0, "lines": ["あ、", "そーだ。"]}], "img_path": "082.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [516, 77, 700, 303], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["Ｒちゃん。", "トトーペーサに", "もし西片が", "曲の火・９月６"]}], "img_path": "083.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [433, 46, 680, 100], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["カリーン"]}, {"box": [684, 702, 748, 839], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["あぁあ", "ああぁー"]}, {"box": [380, 671, 438, 752], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["私の勝ち", "だね。"]}, {"box": [409, 916, 428, 980], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["．．．．．．．．"]}, {"box": [110, 923, 131, 1007], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["ズルいぞ。"]}], "img_path": "084.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [670, 112, 701, 176], "vertical": true, "font_size": 29.0, "lines": ["何が？"]}, {"box": [83, 51, 359, 71], "vertical": false, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["からかいと手の高ホさんの"]}, {"box": [87, 154, 201, 275], "vertical": true, "font_size": 30.0, "lines": ["何って．．．", "今、投げる", "時．．．"]}, {"box": [721, 419, 747, 464], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["ん？"]}, {"box": [429, 427, 463, 476], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["何？"]}, {"box": [359, 430, 377, 474], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["．．．．．"]}, {"box": [104, 450, 153, 527], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["なんでも", "ない．．"]}, {"box": [586, 725, 633, 862], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["さーて", "約束だもんねー"]}, {"box": [480, 748, 534, 885], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["何してもらおう", "かなー。"]}, {"box": [294, 739, 322, 812], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["うーん。"]}, {"box": [498, 983, 516, 1030], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["．．．．．"]}, {"box": [72, 1000, 116, 1095], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["なんだ．．．", "何がくる．．．"]}], "img_path": "085.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [760, 81, 780, 112], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["ま、"]}, {"box": [381, 91, 434, 234], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["別にいいや", "何もしなくても。"]}, {"box": [590, 693, 608, 757], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["．．．．．．？"]}, {"box": [661, 925, 711, 1059], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["いや．．．高木さん", "それは．．．"]}, {"box": [485, 955, 609, 1108], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["そういうこと", "されるとなんか", "一生勝てなくなる", "気がするから", "それは．．．"]}, {"box": [240, 923, 317, 1078], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["どーせ", "勝てないから", "いいんじゃない？"]}], "img_path": "086.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [482, 76, 564, 174], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["日"]}, {"box": [626, 43, 718, 99], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["ちょく"]}], "img_path": "087.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [716, 505, 796, 583], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["あ", "あ、"]}, {"box": [379, 479, 451, 611], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["まったく．．", "めんどうだなぁ", "日直なんて．．．"]}, {"box": [108, 480, 214, 678], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["なんで早く行って", "黒板ふいたり", "日誌書いたり", "しなきゃいけないんだ。"]}, {"box": [386, 938, 459, 1069], "vertical": true, "font_size": 17.0, "lines": ["．．．そうだ。", "どうせならこの", "チャンスに．．"]}, {"box": [113, 952, 195, 1124], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["高木さんの机に", "いたずらを", "しかけておくか．．．！"]}], "img_path": "088.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [641, 94, 716, 191], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["ふふ．．．さいねむ", "少し眠気が", "とんだぞ。"]}, {"box": [670, 908, 697, 1003], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["高木さん．．．"]}, {"box": [142, 888, 196, 987], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["もう来てん", "のか．．．"]}, {"box": [114, 924, 140, 1003], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["なんで．．．？"]}], "img_path": "089.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [534, 536, 598, 610], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["誰も", "いない。"]}, {"box": [285, 527, 335, 644], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["あれ？", "おかしいな．．．"]}, {"box": [93, 528, 148, 662], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["見間違い", "だったのか．．．？"]}], "img_path": "090.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [656, 82, 727, 230], "vertical": true, "font_size": 31.0, "lines": ["いや．．．", "感じるぞ．．．"]}, {"box": [105, 124, 185, 270], "vertical": true, "font_size": 30.0, "lines": ["高木さんの", "気配を．．．"]}, {"box": [646, 676, 746, 810], "vertical": true, "font_size": 28.0, "lines": ["どこかに", "隠れて", "いるな．．．！！"]}, {"box": [316, 639, 420, 813], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["危ない．．．いっえ", "一瞬とはいえ", "油断して鼻歌を", "歌うところだった．．．"]}, {"box": [351, 962, 395, 1040], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["どこだ．．．", "どこに．．．"]}, {"box": [76, 946, 93, 976], "vertical": true, "font_size": 17.0, "lines": ["！"]}], "img_path": "091.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [674, 665, 739, 877], "vertical": true, "font_size": 30.0, "lines": ["ふっ．．．甘い．．．甘いよ", "高木さん．．．"]}, {"box": [441, 664, 517, 769], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["すき間から", "上はきが", "丸見えだよ"]}, {"box": [284, 657, 387, 796], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["黒板をふこうと", "近寄った瞬間に", "驚かせる", "気だろう。"]}, {"box": [142, 658, 220, 765], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["けど、", "そうは", "いかないよ。"]}], "img_path": "092.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [667, 56, 745, 232], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["あーあ。日直の仕事", "めんどくさいから", "やらないでおこー。"]}, {"box": [508, 82, 582, 215], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["黒板とか", "ふかなくても", "バレないしー"]}, {"box": [361, 86, 407, 182], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["どうだい", "高木さん！"]}, {"box": [115, 94, 189, 246], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["企みが失敗して", "きっと悔しがって", "いるんだろうね"]}, {"box": [72, 148, 89, 213], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["フフフ．．．"]}, {"box": [633, 795, 736, 930], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["ああ見たいなぁ", "高木さんの", "悔しがってる顔", "．．．"]}, {"box": [367, 630, 398, 692], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["想像図"]}, {"box": [350, 832, 367, 876], "vertical": true, "font_size": 17.0, "lines": ["．．．"]}, {"box": [104, 805, 156, 873], "vertical": true, "font_size": 27.0, "lines": ["いや", "待てよ、"]}], "img_path": "093.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [617, 105, 765, 303], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["考えてもみろ．．．", "あの高木さんが", "上はき丸見えなんて", "そんなミスを", "するだろうか．．．"]}, {"box": [270, 0, 538, 159], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["最新設備"]}, {"box": [112, 128, 199, 250], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["いや！", "しない。"]}, {"box": [606, 394, 723, 500], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["語"]}, {"box": [678, 558, 734, 741], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["つまり", "あれはフェイク！"]}, {"box": [302, 563, 355, 679], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["危ないところ", "だった．．．！"]}, {"box": [100, 557, 153, 678], "vertical": true, "font_size": 30.0, "lines": ["さすが", "高木さんだ．．．"]}, {"box": [699, 901, 742, 1012], "vertical": true, "font_size": 16.0, "lines": ["さて：どこに", "いるんだ"]}, {"box": [435, 890, 512, 1061], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["高木さんのことだ。", "いないなんてことは", "ないはず．．．"]}], "img_path": "094.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [719, 63, 746, 159], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["廊下には．．．"]}, {"box": [523, 59, 542, 197], "vertical": true, "font_size": 17.0, "lines": ["いないようだな。"]}, {"box": [695, 447, 741, 525], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["となると", "残りは．．．"]}, {"box": [666, 939, 745, 1086], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["あー", "トイレでも", "行ってくるかぁ。"]}, {"box": [331, 935, 390, 1016], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["驚かせて", "やる．．．"]}, {"box": [97, 1024, 126, 1076], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["そち"]}], "img_path": "095.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [651, 355, 745, 733], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["ここだぁ！！！"]}, {"box": [290, 853, 378, 996], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["い．．．", "いない！"]}], "img_path": "096.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [603, 733, 751, 1026], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["オレは一体．．．", "何をやっていたん", "だろうなぁ．．"]}], "img_path": "097.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [666, 54, 759, 290], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["わっ！！"]}, {"box": [89, 43, 210, 385], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["うわぁ！！"]}, {"box": [698, 776, 741, 993], "vertical": true, "font_size": 30.0, "lines": ["うわっ！！", "わ．．．"]}, {"box": [365, 778, 415, 858], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["あははだ．．．", "大丈夫？"]}, {"box": [260, 772, 308, 907], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["カ．．．カーテンの", "裏に．．．"]}], "img_path": "098.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [692, 62, 738, 196], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["わかんなかった", "でしょ。"]}, {"box": [344, 84, 417, 264], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["このカーテン", "ちょっと透けるから", "全部見えてたんだよ。"]}, {"box": [62, 412, 149, 552], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["ちくしょう．．", "嬉しそうな顔", "してんなぁ．．．"]}, {"box": [695, 685, 745, 840], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["あぁ", "おもしろかった："]}, {"box": [459, 696, 542, 795], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["西片の行動", "思い出した", "だけで．．．"]}, {"box": [397, 746, 422, 834], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["ぷくくく。"]}, {"box": [237, 679, 291, 843], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["早起きした", "かいがあったよー。"]}, {"box": [370, 970, 387, 1031], "vertical": true, "font_size": 17.0, "lines": ["く．．．．．．"]}, {"box": [116, 912, 172, 1003], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["このため", "だけに！？"]}], "img_path": "099.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [746, 227, 793, 342], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["くそ．．．", "高木さんめ．．．"]}, {"box": [420, 72, 449, 159], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["ねぇ西片。"]}, {"box": [636, 507, 780, 672], "vertical": true, "font_size": 29.0, "lines": ["なんか", "静かな教室で", "二人っきり", "だとさー、"]}, {"box": [199, 509, 311, 700], "vertical": true, "font_size": 28.0, "lines": ["世界に二人しか", "いない感じ", "しない？"]}], "img_path": "100.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [299, 160, 401, 319], "vertical": true, "font_size": 27.0, "lines": ["このまま", "誰も来なきゃ", "いいのにね。"]}, {"box": [582, 685, 715, 785], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["あの．．．たかぎ", "高木さん．．．"]}, {"box": [350, 689, 433, 807], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["高木さんて．．．", "もしかして．．", "オ．．．"]}, {"box": [179, 680, 200, 796], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["オレのこと．．．"]}], "img_path": "101.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [739, 90, 767, 255], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["おっはよー！"]}, {"box": [226, 127, 281, 230], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["いい天気", "だねーー！"]}, {"box": [92, 380, 194, 515], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["もーなんで", "朝からそんなに", "テンション", "高いのよ。"]}, {"box": [725, 575, 772, 671], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["ホントに．．", "ウザイ．．"]}, {"box": [563, 576, 640, 700], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["いたた！", "痛いよ", "サナエちゃん。"]}, {"box": [719, 793, 733, 810], "vertical": true, "font_size": 17.0, "lines": ["！"]}, {"box": [690, 752, 736, 856], "vertical": true, "font_size": 17.0, "lines": ["もー", "やめなって。"]}, {"box": [370, 614, 422, 714], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["なんだっけ", "西片。"]}, {"box": [214, 584, 261, 680], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["．．．なんでも", "．．．ない．．．"]}, {"box": [100, 588, 125, 656], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["ふーん。"]}, {"box": [576, 980, 650, 1122], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["そういえば", "西片、", "日直の仕事は？"]}, {"box": [217, 998, 278, 1117], "vertical": true, "font_size": 27.0, "lines": ["あぁ！？", "忘れてた！"]}], "img_path": "102.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [77, 17, 185, 132], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["かさ", "傘"]}], "img_path": "103.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [690, 410, 796, 535], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["げ。", "ちょうど", "下校時間に", "降りだしたか。"]}, {"box": [531, 437, 555, 479], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["え？！"]}, {"box": [419, 414, 470, 548], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["雨なんて", "聞いてないよ！"]}, {"box": [104, 426, 184, 550], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["私、カッパ", "持ってきて", "ないんだけど。"]}, {"box": [441, 650, 468, 704], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["ドジ。"]}, {"box": [110, 652, 158, 768], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["じゃあ", "バスで帰る？"]}, {"box": [692, 898, 745, 1034], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["バス代なんて", "持ってないよ！"]}, {"box": [562, 903, 615, 983], "vertical": true, "font_size": 28.0, "lines": ["すっごい", "ドジ。"]}, {"box": [311, 904, 388, 1030], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["貸して", "あげるよ．．．", "バス代ぐらい。"]}], "img_path": "104.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [709, 121, 731, 183], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["くそ．．．"]}, {"box": [482, 103, 568, 267], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["今日も", "さんざん", "からかわれたなぁ。"]}, {"box": [80, 50, 371, 73], "vertical": false, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["からかい上手の高木さんの"]}, {"box": [371, 386, 424, 501], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["帰らないの？", "高木さん"]}, {"box": [684, 651, 708, 729], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["いやー．．．"]}, {"box": [123, 670, 209, 816], "vertical": true, "font_size": 29.0, "lines": ["傘も", "カッパも", "忘れちゃってさ。"]}, {"box": [331, 1071, 363, 1121], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["フッ"]}, {"box": [192, 952, 227, 969], "vertical": false, "font_size": 17.0, "lines": ["やれいけど"]}], "img_path": "105.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [660, 62, 804, 250], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["バハハハ！", "ドジだね", "高木さん！"]}, {"box": [107, 37, 260, 407], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["今日は雨だと", "知らなかったのかい！？", "ドジだねぇ！？"]}, {"box": [562, 917, 664, 1041], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["たしか", "西片の傘って", "ちょっと", "大きめだよね。"]}, {"box": [207, 951, 234, 1004], "vertical": true, "font_size": 27.0, "lines": ["え？"]}], "img_path": "106.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [216, 49, 289, 276], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["これは相合い傘と", "いうやつでは．．．"]}, {"box": [85, 83, 155, 274], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["なぜ", "こんなコトに！"]}, {"box": [640, 833, 746, 929], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["高木さん", "自転車は", "どうすんの", "．．．？"]}, {"box": [388, 825, 471, 935], "vertical": true, "font_size": 28.0, "lines": ["明日は", "歩いておいて", "学校行くよ。"]}, {"box": [328, 829, 357, 864], "vertical": true, "font_size": 29.0, "lines": ["あ、"]}, {"box": [97, 1042, 115, 1102], "vertical": true, "font_size": 17.0, "lines": ["そう．．．"]}], "img_path": "107.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [627, 106, 756, 260], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["く．．．なんだか今", "とてつもなく", "恥ずかしいことを", "している", "気分だ．．．"]}, {"box": [408, 121, 488, 225], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["息が．．．いき", "息が", "しにくい．．"]}, {"box": [287, 121, 360, 274], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["なんとかして気を", "まぎらわせ", "ないと．．．"]}, {"box": [538, 932, 566, 1016], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["高木さん。"]}], "img_path": "108.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [271, 63, 359, 269], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["！！", "どうだー", "カエルの苦手な", "女子は多いと聞く！"]}, {"box": [93, 350, 156, 466], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["驚くがいい", "高木さん！"]}, {"box": [344, 723, 397, 810], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["へー", "かわいー。"]}, {"box": [110, 738, 155, 832], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["なんだって", "ええ．．．？"]}], "img_path": "109.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [677, 125, 750, 241], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["くそ．．．", "さすが", "高木さんだ．．．"]}, {"box": [571, 127, 620, 207], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["この程度", "では．．"]}, {"box": [680, 689, 705, 781], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["うわあ！"]}, {"box": [495, 699, 513, 783], "vertical": true, "font_size": 16.0, "lines": ["あははは。"]}, {"box": [394, 695, 421, 816], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["驚きすぎだよ、"]}, {"box": [123, 718, 145, 827], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["あははは！"]}], "img_path": "110.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [659, 108, 738, 228], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["ところで西片", "そっちの肩", "濡れてない？"]}, {"box": [551, 69, 598, 186], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["ちゃんと", "傘入ってる？"]}, {"box": [365, 96, 442, 212], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["ああ．．．", "ちょっとだし", "いいよ。"]}, {"box": [155, 148, 230, 273], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["ダメだよ。", "また風邪", "引いちゃうよ。"]}, {"box": [148, 526, 195, 649], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["もうちょっと", "くっつくから、"]}, {"box": [56, 655, 101, 753], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["ちゃんと傘", "入りなよ。"]}], "img_path": "111.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [692, 108, 729, 172], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["し．．．"]}, {"box": [179, 267, 294, 383], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["心臓の", "音が．．．", "すごい．．"]}, {"box": [711, 614, 738, 711], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["落ち着け．．．"]}, {"box": [368, 625, 466, 817], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["キンチョーしてるのが", "高木さんにバレたら", "またからかわれて", "しまうぞ．．．！！"]}, {"box": [111, 590, 161, 723], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["とにかく何か．．", "しゃべろう！"]}, {"box": [276, 951, 304, 1048], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["高木さん．．．"]}], "img_path": "112.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [644, 119, 721, 262], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["珍しいよね、", "高木さんが", "忘れ物なんてさ。"]}, {"box": [320, 121, 390, 274], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["いやーいつも", "ちゃんとしてると", "思ってたけど、"]}, {"box": [84, 51, 354, 71], "vertical": false, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["からかいと手の高ホさんは"]}, {"box": [219, 116, 238, 221], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["まさかだよ。"]}, {"box": [558, 480, 749, 703], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["もしかして", "高木さんって", "案外ドジ", "なのかいっ！？"]}, {"box": [96, 324, 114, 387], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["．．．．．．？"]}, {"box": [99, 901, 124, 962], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["んー．．．"]}], "img_path": "113.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [575, 91, 648, 244], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["そうだねー", "たしかにちょっと", "忘れっぽいかも。"]}, {"box": [309, 453, 334, 558], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["おぉ．．．！？"]}, {"box": [640, 672, 745, 789], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["高木さんがじゃ", "自分で", "忘れっぽいと", "認めた．．．！？"]}, {"box": [130, 656, 174, 770], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["なんだ．．．", "この気分は．．．"]}, {"box": [689, 926, 722, 1061], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["すっごく"]}, {"box": [154, 924, 203, 1130], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["勝った気分！"]}], "img_path": "114.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [651, 120, 730, 283], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["今もちょっと", "ド忘れしてる", "言葉があってさー。"]}, {"box": [297, 117, 351, 221], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["へえ", "ド忘れねぇ、"]}, {"box": [85, 51, 356, 71], "vertical": false, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["からかいと手の高ホさん"]}, {"box": [359, 397, 489, 618], "vertical": true, "font_size": 29.0, "lines": ["今、二人で", "一つの傘使ってる", "この状況って", "なんて言うんだっけ。"]}, {"box": [110, 258, 128, 373], "vertical": true, "font_size": 16.0, "lines": ["どんなコト？"]}, {"box": [722, 966, 745, 1008], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["え．．．"]}, {"box": [400, 931, 420, 1016], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["ちょっと、"]}, {"box": [104, 919, 155, 1044], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["ド忘れ", "しちゃってさ。"]}], "img_path": "115.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [508, 87, 557, 167], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["あ．．．あ", "えっと．．．"]}, {"box": [440, 98, 458, 204], "vertical": true, "font_size": 16.0, "lines": ["あいあいがさ。"]}, {"box": [121, 133, 149, 223], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["え？何？"]}, {"box": [572, 510, 622, 606], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["聞こえない", "なあ～～～"]}, {"box": [611, 957, 688, 1065], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["あ！お！", "思い出した、", "相合い傘だ。"]}, {"box": [201, 951, 288, 1071], "vertical": true, "font_size": 31.0, "lines": ["絶対", "忘れて", "なかったろ！"]}], "img_path": "116.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [659, 106, 734, 229], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["あとさ", "あれ、なんて", "言うんだっけ。"]}, {"box": [475, 99, 575, 254], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["カップルが", "愛情表現のために", "唇と唇を", "くっつけるやつ。"]}, {"box": [413, 251, 436, 336], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["キ．．．キス。"]}, {"box": [96, 301, 123, 390], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["え？何？"]}, {"box": [577, 630, 682, 727], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["聞こえない", "フリしない", "でよ！！", "高木さん！"]}, {"box": [215, 635, 267, 698], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["あはは", "はは。"]}], "img_path": "117.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [692, 73, 750, 167], "vertical": true, "font_size": 29.0, "lines": ["雨", "止んだね。"]}, {"box": [508, 85, 528, 188], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["ホントだね。"]}, {"box": [234, 91, 332, 226], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["よかった．．．", "高木さんちまで", "続くかと思って", "ヒヤヒヤした．．"]}, {"box": [677, 607, 747, 738], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["じゃ．．．じゃあ", "高木さん、オレ", "こっちだから、"]}, {"box": [448, 603, 469, 672], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["またね。"]}, {"box": [562, 914, 643, 1058], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["帰り道", "ド忘れ", "しちゃったなぁ。"]}, {"box": [197, 923, 275, 1041], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["もう", "カンベン", "してよぉお！"]}], "img_path": "118.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [256, 130, 509, 266], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["風", "邪"]}], "img_path": "119.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [617, 138, 668, 243], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["～～～", "こうなると、"]}, {"box": [134, 80, 181, 176], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["こうなるん", "だぞ！"]}, {"box": [641, 437, 694, 563], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["覚えて", "おくようにー。"]}], "img_path": "120.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [365, 138, 411, 262], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["おはよう", "ございまーす。"]}, {"box": [202, 121, 308, 246], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["おう西片、", "今日は風邪で", "休むんじゃ", "なかったのか。"]}, {"box": [111, 145, 127, 239], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["大丈夫か？"]}, {"box": [96, 494, 146, 582], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["はい、", "なんとか。"]}, {"box": [322, 718, 397, 819], "vertical": true, "font_size": 29.0, "lines": ["おはよ、", "風邪", "引いたの？"]}, {"box": [59, 705, 108, 813], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["あぁ", "ちょっとね。"]}, {"box": [73, 1030, 98, 1115], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["ーん。", "ふー"]}], "img_path": "121.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [634, 134, 760, 307], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["夜更かしして", "深夜アニメの", "「１００％片想い」", "観てるからだよ。"]}, {"box": [108, 120, 218, 283], "vertical": true, "font_size": 30.0, "lines": ["ちょっと声が", "デカいよ！", "高木さん。"]}, {"box": [522, 597, 544, 655], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["あだっ"]}, {"box": [425, 594, 476, 730], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["声がデカいのは", "お前だ！"]}, {"box": [219, 859, 386, 902], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["ゴホゴホ"]}, {"box": [110, 591, 161, 699], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["す．．．", "すいません。"]}, {"box": [427, 876, 500, 973], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["ちょっと．．．", "ひどいよ", "高木さん。"]}], "img_path": "122.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [589, 77, 646, 157], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["大丈夫？", "西片．．．"]}, {"box": [374, 72, 426, 177], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["あぁ．．．", "大丈夫だよ。"]}, {"box": [627, 485, 728, 601], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["くそ．．．", "さっそく", "からかわれて", "しまったぞ．．．"]}, {"box": [126, 488, 207, 641], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["風邪引いてるって", "いうのに", "容赦ないな！"]}, {"box": [657, 805, 685, 914], "vertical": true, "font_size": 28.0, "lines": ["しかし！"]}, {"box": [74, 821, 185, 1039], "vertical": true, "font_size": 31.0, "lines": ["今日オレには", "とっておきの", "秘策があるのさ！！"]}], "img_path": "123.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [513, 182, 617, 297], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["なんでおかいしゃ", "部外者が", "こんなとこに", "いるの！？"]}, {"box": [399, 113, 476, 267], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["もう怒った！", "私あの人に", "文句言ってくる！"]}, {"box": [406, 430, 436, 500], "vertical": true, "font_size": 30.0, "lines": ["あの！"]}, {"box": [269, 683, 345, 805], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["キミ", "可愛いね。"]}], "img_path": "124.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [547, 66, 601, 181], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["おっと失礼", "何か用かい？"]}, {"box": [70, 30, 156, 453], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["これは使える！"]}, {"box": [593, 391, 646, 453], "vertical": true, "font_size": 28.0, "lines": ["いえ", "あの．．．"]}, {"box": [692, 535, 745, 619], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["風邪は", "引いたが、"]}, {"box": [507, 556, 632, 653], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["得たものの", "大きさから", "したら", "ちっぽけな", "もんさ．．．"]}, {"box": [622, 730, 732, 974], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["さあ高木さん", "オレをからかおうと", "するがいい。"]}, {"box": [74, 748, 178, 912], "vertical": true, "font_size": 31.0, "lines": ["カウンターで", "赤面させて", "やる！"]}], "img_path": "125.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [], "img_path": "126.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [693, 124, 747, 189], "vertical": true, "font_size": 28.0, "lines": ["さあ", "こい！"]}, {"box": [476, 141, 527, 222], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["いつでも", "ＯＫさ！"]}, {"box": [82, 48, 358, 73], "vertical": false, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["からかい上手の高ホさんの"]}, {"box": [274, 699, 342, 760], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["え？何？"]}, {"box": [127, 682, 189, 772], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["別に", "なんでも。"]}], "img_path": "127.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [657, 169, 688, 239], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["１５分後"]}, {"box": [123, 250, 190, 441], "vertical": true, "font_size": 28.0, "lines": ["おかしい．．", "なぜこない．．．？"]}, {"box": [680, 707, 749, 821], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["そろそろ", "このポーズも", "ツラいのに．．．"]}, {"box": [549, 704, 623, 821], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["っていうか", "板書", "できないし．．．"]}, {"box": [376, 677, 480, 870], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["ハッ！？", "まさか！", "このポーズのせいで", "気づかれているのか？"]}, {"box": [103, 698, 176, 848], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["カウンターを", "くらわせようと", "していることが！"]}, {"box": [106, 980, 159, 1117], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["普通に", "座っておこう．．"]}], "img_path": "128.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [622, 600, 725, 762], "vertical": true, "font_size": 27.0, "lines": ["どうしたって", "いうんだい！？", "高木さん．．．"]}, {"box": [610, 952, 712, 1105], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["いつもなら", "もう３回は", "からかってきてる", "ハズなのに．．．"]}, {"box": [117, 971, 171, 1105], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["風邪でも", "引いてるのか？"]}], "img_path": "129.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [667, 760, 730, 900], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["．．．高木さんて", "黙ってると．．．"]}, {"box": [99, 1065, 134, 1103], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["！？"]}], "img_path": "130.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [84, 51, 354, 71], "vertical": false, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["からかいと手の高ホさんは"]}, {"box": [671, 854, 704, 965], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["ヤバイ．．．"]}, {"box": [98, 841, 255, 1094], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["急に．．．", "カウンターの", "「カワイイね」を言うのが", "もの凄く恥ずかしく", "なってきたぞ．．．！"]}], "img_path": "131.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [370, 119, 483, 255], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["いや大体", "言えるわけ", "ないだろ！？"]}, {"box": [219, 78, 297, 253], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["夜更かしからくる", "睡眠不足と風邪で", "どうかしてたのか．．．"]}, {"box": [370, 385, 438, 493], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["バカか", "オレは！"]}, {"box": [419, 568, 470, 686], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["どうかした？", "西片。"]}, {"box": [367, 847, 388, 930], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["ちょっと、"]}, {"box": [691, 868, 741, 966], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["い．．．いや", "なんでも．．．"]}, {"box": [111, 871, 167, 952], "vertical": true, "font_size": 30.0, "lines": ["顔", "赤いよ？"]}], "img_path": "132.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [705, 71, 729, 105], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["え。"]}, {"box": [394, 144, 446, 276], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["大丈夫？", "しんどくない？"]}, {"box": [281, 151, 338, 233], "vertical": true, "font_size": 28.0, "lines": ["大丈夫", "大丈夫！"]}, {"box": [415, 412, 452, 473], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["だ．．"]}, {"box": [146, 353, 199, 489], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["でも顔赤いよ。", "熱あるの？"]}, {"box": [635, 621, 739, 758], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["なんで今日は", "そんなに", "優しいんだよ！", "高木さん．．．"]}, {"box": [469, 609, 543, 787], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["いやいや", "ホントに", "なんでもないんだよ。"]}, {"box": [320, 607, 419, 780], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["「カワイイ」とか", "言おうとしてたのが", "ますます恥ずかしく", "なってきたぞ．．．！"]}, {"box": [114, 619, 133, 714], "vertical": true, "font_size": 17.0, "lines": ["ホントに？"]}, {"box": [97, 987, 146, 1064], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["ホント", "ホント！"]}], "img_path": "133.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [723, 79, 795, 232], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["むしろ風邪だって", "ほとんど言い訳", "みたいなもんで！"]}, {"box": [604, 84, 678, 237], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["起きた時には", "もう８時半で", "それで遅刻して！"]}, {"box": [442, 94, 487, 210], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["だからホント", "大丈夫だよ！"]}, {"box": [320, 87, 373, 195], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["じゃあ別に", "元気なんだ。"]}, {"box": [101, 314, 158, 413], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["うん。全然", "平気だよ。"]}, {"box": [644, 966, 721, 1083], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["じゃあ", "からかっても", "いいんだね。"]}, {"box": [390, 967, 449, 1060], "vertical": true, "font_size": 27.0, "lines": ["えぇ！？", "何それ！"]}, {"box": [152, 960, 230, 1093], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["この日は", "いつもより沢山", "からかわれた。"]}], "img_path": "134.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [234, 96, 624, 233], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["ほん", "本屋さん"]}], "img_path": "135.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [699, 549, 728, 665], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["誰も来るな．．．"]}, {"box": [413, 546, 440, 662], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["誰も来るな！！"]}, {"box": [686, 867, 743, 948], "vertical": true, "font_size": 28.0, "lines": ["４２０円に", "なりま．．．"]}, {"box": [451, 867, 498, 987], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["あ、ちょうど", "いただきます。"]}, {"box": [358, 868, 378, 964], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["カバーは．．．"]}, {"box": [256, 858, 276, 965], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["いりません！！"]}, {"box": [112, 878, 133, 992], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["レシートも！！"]}], "img_path": "136.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [83, 77, 139, 417], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["手に：入れた．．．！！"]}, {"box": [113, 516, 218, 671], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["あまり人のいない", "本屋さんを選んで", "朝一で来たのは", "正解だった．．．！！"]}, {"box": [648, 532, 720, 683], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["よし．．．やったぞ．．．", "誰にも見られて", "いない．．．！！"]}, {"box": [619, 883, 746, 1055], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["しかもおつりを", "出す時間を", "なくすために", "金もぴったり用意．．．", "さすがだオレ．．．！！"]}, {"box": [308, 892, 379, 1007], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["さて．．．あとは", "帰ってコレを", "ゆっくりと．．．"]}, {"box": [295, 1048, 324, 1200], "vertical": true, "font_size": 29.0, "lines": ["．．．"]}], "img_path": "137.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [412, 75, 487, 175], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["おはよ、", "西片。"]}, {"box": [385, 711, 464, 810], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["高木さん！？", "どうして", "ここに！？"]}, {"box": [98, 706, 160, 800], "vertical": true, "font_size": 29.0, "lines": ["散歩", "してるの。"]}, {"box": [393, 991, 456, 1088], "vertical": true, "font_size": 27.0, "lines": ["心を．．．．．．", "読んだ！？"]}], "img_path": "138.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [685, 103, 738, 219], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["西片は", "何してんの？"]}, {"box": [452, 110, 473, 187], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["く．．．っ．．"]}, {"box": [84, 51, 359, 71], "vertical": false, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["からかいと手の高ホさんの"]}, {"box": [107, 104, 181, 258], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["ここは", "どうやっても", "ごまかさねば．．．！！"]}, {"box": [433, 281, 477, 472], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["これを見られでも", "したら：オレはもう．．．"]}, {"box": [663, 576, 739, 718], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["いやあ", "欲しい本が", "あったんだけど、"]}, {"box": [405, 583, 453, 663], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["あいにく", "売り切．．．"]}, {"box": [281, 568, 356, 655], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["待て", "待て！！"]}, {"box": [640, 875, 738, 1010], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["もしかして", "レジにいる所を", "見られている", "可能性も．．．！！"]}, {"box": [119, 829, 193, 1038], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["だとしたら", "今のまましゃべってたら", "完全にアウトだったな。"]}], "img_path": "139.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [693, 132, 727, 220], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["ば．．．．．"]}, {"box": [128, 157, 207, 318], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["爆裂！！．．．", "最強サッカー！！", "１１巻を買いまして。"]}, {"box": [606, 482, 731, 619], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["どうだ！！", "男子にはいにんき", "大人気だけど", "女子はあまり", "興味ないだろ！"]}, {"box": [508, 489, 552, 645], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["いろいろと", "カンペキな返答だ。"]}, {"box": [387, 505, 441, 601], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["今のオレは", "冴えて．．．"]}, {"box": [115, 480, 194, 614], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["へぇー、よく", "男子が話してる", "やつだよねー。"]}, {"box": [407, 911, 451, 1020], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["見せて。"]}], "img_path": "140.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [639, 124, 713, 248], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["あ．．．いや～～", "あのオレまだ", "読んでないし。"]}, {"box": [391, 113, 490, 295], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["どんなのか", "知りたいだけだから。", "なんなら表紙", "だけでも。"]}, {"box": [282, 119, 329, 215], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["ムリムリ！", "絶対ムリ！！"]}, {"box": [82, 51, 357, 71], "vertical": false, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["からかいと手の高ホさんは"]}, {"box": [156, 107, 230, 242], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["オレだってまだ", "表紙ちゃんと", "見てないもん！！"]}, {"box": [91, 305, 143, 421], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["じゃあ一緒に", "見ようよ。"]}, {"box": [102, 493, 181, 611], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["オレ、一人で", "見るタイプ", "だからさぁ！！"]}, {"box": [693, 691, 718, 773], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["ちぇ"]}, {"box": [176, 682, 249, 814], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["まさかこんなに", "食いついてくる", "なんて．．．"]}, {"box": [111, 720, 131, 877], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["なんて危険な人だ。"]}, {"box": [629, 953, 683, 1114], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["ここは早く", "離れた方がいいな。"]}, {"box": [124, 959, 177, 1102], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["じゃあ高木さん、", "オレ．．．帰るから。"]}], "img_path": "141.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [381, 112, 402, 189], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["あの．．．？"]}, {"box": [125, 97, 202, 251], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["せっかく会ったん", "だし、ちょっと", "一緒に歩こうよ。"]}, {"box": [376, 471, 404, 532], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["あ．．．"]}, {"box": [107, 485, 132, 554], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["う．．．ん。"]}], "img_path": "142.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [607, 100, 735, 292], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["く．．．．．", "このリュックの中に", "絶対に見られては", "いけないものが", "入っていると思うと．．．"]}, {"box": [376, 112, 431, 227], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["生きた心地が", "しない．．．！！"]}, {"box": [80, 50, 349, 72], "vertical": false, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["からかい上手の高ホさん"]}, {"box": [251, 108, 308, 233], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["早く．．．", "家に帰りたい。"]}, {"box": [247, 506, 276, 560], "vertical": true, "font_size": 30.0, "lines": ["ねえ、"]}, {"box": [180, 535, 212, 588], "vertical": true, "font_size": 30.0, "lines": ["西片。"]}, {"box": [339, 704, 422, 894], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["私にウソ", "ついてない？"]}], "img_path": "143.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [746, 75, 781, 135], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["あ．．．"]}, {"box": [429, 84, 461, 146], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["ウソ、"]}, {"box": [113, 165, 136, 281], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["ついてる？"]}, {"box": [533, 426, 557, 507], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["え．．．？"]}, {"box": [431, 385, 450, 479], "vertical": true, "font_size": 16.0, "lines": ["あ．．．あの．．．"]}, {"box": [625, 610, 703, 764], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["買ったの．．．", "爆裂なんとかじゃ", "ないでしょ。"]}, {"box": [146, 642, 164, 707], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["．．．．．．？"]}, {"box": [625, 888, 725, 1021], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["ウソついてまで", "隠すような", "恥ずかしいもの", "買ったの？"]}, {"box": [139, 938, 186, 1016], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["いや．．．", "えーと．．．"]}], "img_path": "144.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [679, 77, 732, 251], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["普通の", "恋愛まんがでしょ？"]}, {"box": [378, 60, 430, 370], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["『１００％片想い』って。"]}, {"box": [118, 140, 165, 272], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["いや．．．まぁ", "そうなんです"]}, {"box": [101, 403, 123, 468], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["け．．．ど、"]}, {"box": [550, 667, 626, 884], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["なんで", "知ってんのォ！？"]}, {"box": [257, 649, 329, 805], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["いやーたまたま", "通りかかったら", "西片がレジにいて、"]}, {"box": [142, 655, 187, 774], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["タイトル", "見えちゃった。"]}, {"box": [113, 942, 194, 1073], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["知ってて今まで", "もてあそんで", "いたのか．．．！"]}], "img_path": "145.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [684, 105, 735, 281], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["西片、そういうのも", "好きなんだねー。"]}, {"box": [414, 112, 462, 198], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["あの．．．たかぎ", "高木さん、"]}, {"box": [111, 117, 189, 270], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["このことは誰にも", "言わないで", "もらえますか："]}, {"box": [351, 393, 453, 602], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["こういうの読んでるって", "知られたら．．．", "きっと男子の中で", "笑われてしまうので．．．"]}, {"box": [113, 408, 138, 471], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["んー"]}, {"box": [713, 721, 733, 883], "vertical": true, "font_size": 16.0, "lines": ["どうしよっかなー"]}, {"box": [489, 734, 569, 869], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["西片、私に", "ウソついたから", "なー"]}, {"box": [345, 734, 425, 867], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["私なんて西片に", "ウソついたコト", "ないのにさー。"]}, {"box": [194, 716, 249, 851], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["ゴ．．", "ゴメンなさい"]}, {"box": [104, 754, 151, 866], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["あの．．．", "なにとぞ．．．"]}], "img_path": "146.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [676, 87, 721, 190], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["わかった", "言わないよ。"]}, {"box": [518, 96, 565, 220], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["え！？そんなに", "アッサリ！？"]}, {"box": [432, 76, 463, 139], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["何が？"]}, {"box": [107, 65, 152, 215], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["ポントのホントに", "言わないでよ！？"]}, {"box": [706, 475, 728, 596], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["しつこいなー、"]}, {"box": [627, 481, 659, 516], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["あ、"]}, {"box": [574, 459, 590, 608], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["じゃあこうしよう。"]}, {"box": [400, 297, 452, 366], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["うん", "いいよ。"]}, {"box": [428, 480, 510, 622], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["私も西片に", "私のヒミツを", "教えてあげるよ。"]}, {"box": [111, 291, 185, 406], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["ホントに！？", "なんか軽いよ", "高木さん！！"]}, {"box": [74, 472, 150, 623], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["お互いの", "ヒミツ知ってたら", "少しは安心でしょ。"]}, {"box": [650, 936, 701, 1024], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["え？", "あ．．．うん。"]}, {"box": [502, 976, 550, 1061], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["じゃあ", "耳貸して。"]}, {"box": [123, 918, 143, 996], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["あのね．．．"]}], "img_path": "147.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [361, 128, 448, 333], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["私西片のこと", "好きだよ。"]}], "img_path": "148.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [679, 128, 741, 206], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["え．．．", "ええ！？"]}, {"box": [480, 121, 543, 239], "vertical": true, "font_size": 27.0, "lines": ["高木さん！？", "．．．ええ！？"]}, {"box": [275, 118, 401, 234], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["あはは！", "顔真っ赤！！", "ホントすぐに", "赤くなるね", "西片は！！"]}, {"box": [83, 51, 351, 71], "vertical": false, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["からかい上手の高ホさん"]}, {"box": [156, 183, 182, 248], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["．．．？"]}, {"box": [74, 255, 93, 284], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["？"]}, {"box": [482, 404, 540, 488], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["聞き", "間違い？"]}, {"box": [617, 604, 712, 729], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["西片が", "私にウソ", "ついたから、"]}, {"box": [537, 834, 563, 883], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["．．．あ"]}, {"box": [287, 837, 308, 904], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["あはは。"]}, {"box": [123, 569, 186, 764], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["私もお返しに", "ウソついたんだよ。"]}, {"box": [106, 853, 158, 942], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["うん、", "ウソだよ。"]}, {"box": [725, 990, 747, 1031], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["え．．．"]}, {"box": [422, 836, 470, 979], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["あぁウソか！", "ビックリしたよ。"]}], "img_path": "149.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [690, 104, 739, 256], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["ウソに決まってる", "てしょー。"]}, {"box": [585, 123, 608, 209], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["だよねー。"]}, {"box": [279, 86, 380, 218], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["ヒミツ", "なんかじゃ", "ないもん"]}, {"box": [555, 562, 629, 638], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["じゃ、", "私こっち", "だから。"]}, {"box": [283, 563, 307, 657], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["バイバイ．．．"]}, {"box": [220, 570, 238, 654], "vertical": true, "font_size": 16.0, "lines": ["ウソ．．．か"]}, {"box": [42, 699, 69, 1078], "vertical": true, "font_size": 27.0, "lines": ["１からかい上手の高木さん聞い完上"]}, {"box": [550, 904, 677, 1093], "vertical": true, "font_size": 28.0, "lines": ["あ、西片ー！", "私も１００％片想い』", "読んでみたいから", "今度貸してよー。"]}, {"box": [198, 914, 289, 1054], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["ちょっと、", "声がでかいよ", "高木さん！！！"]}], "img_path": "150.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [], "img_path": "151.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [448, 84, 750, 226], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["おまけ"]}], "img_path": "152.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [681, 100, 736, 220], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["あの二人って", "さー、"]}, {"box": [575, 152, 625, 268], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["付き合ってる", "のかなー。"]}, {"box": [289, 120, 328, 173], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["何？"]}, {"box": [84, 51, 357, 71], "vertical": false, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["からかいと手の高ホさん"]}, {"box": [114, 117, 167, 241], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["西片君と", "高木ちゃんよ。"]}, {"box": [646, 338, 736, 400], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["女子トイレ"]}, {"box": [670, 536, 698, 588], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["さぁ。"]}, {"box": [234, 537, 281, 651], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["気にならない", "わけ？"]}, {"box": [531, 789, 578, 942], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["ユカリ、アンタ", "うらやましいの？"]}, {"box": [113, 569, 160, 711], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["すっごく", "仲良さそうだし。"]}, {"box": [106, 806, 181, 978], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["いや、だってさー．．．", "うらやましいって", "いうか．．．"]}], "img_path": "153.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [640, 120, 715, 300], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["ミナー、ユカリって", "男子と１チャイチャ", "したいんだってさー。"]}, {"box": [370, 173, 418, 250], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["やめてよ", "もう！！"]}, {"box": [263, 113, 311, 230], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["ミナ！！", "聞いてんの！？"]}, {"box": [105, 121, 123, 184], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["うーー"]}, {"box": [287, 529, 365, 652], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["まーだ出て", "なかったの？", "早くしなよー。"]}, {"box": [123, 362, 142, 439], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["ミナー！！"]}, {"box": [654, 537, 726, 718], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["もう！！サナエちゃん", "急に話しかけ", "ないでよ！！"]}, {"box": [439, 536, 515, 708], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["おしっこ出そう", "だったのに", "止まっちゃったよ！！！"]}, {"box": [111, 549, 183, 703], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["やめてよー！！", "集中しないと", "出ないんだから！！"]}, {"box": [590, 956, 724, 1080], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["集中しないと", "出ない", "くらいなら", "しなくても", "いいでしょー。"]}, {"box": [130, 960, 229, 1076], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["このカンジは", "次の授業中に", "くるカンジ", "なの！！"]}], "img_path": "154.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [675, 120, 721, 263], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["もー．．．", "やめなよサナエ。"]}, {"box": [344, 113, 389, 285], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["だってジャマしたく", "なるんだもん。"]}, {"box": [83, 51, 281, 71], "vertical": false, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["からかい上手の高い"]}, {"box": [226, 117, 273, 270], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["なんでアンタは", "いつもそうなの．．．"]}, {"box": [593, 453, 620, 577], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["高木ちゃーん。"]}, {"box": [657, 798, 732, 915], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["ん？", "そんなとこで", "何してんの？"]}, {"box": [407, 813, 455, 956], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["ミナのおしっこ", "ひっこめてんの。"]}, {"box": [126, 939, 149, 1062], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["やーめーてー。"]}], "img_path": "155.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [619, 112, 720, 267], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["ところで、", "高木ちゃんと", "西片君て", "付き合ってんの？"]}, {"box": [487, 100, 540, 199], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["って、", "ユカリが．．．"]}, {"box": [352, 123, 377, 191], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["んーん"]}, {"box": [107, 128, 165, 226], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["付き合って", "ないよ。"]}, {"box": [439, 355, 459, 434], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["．．．ちょ！！"]}, {"box": [616, 551, 721, 658], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["そっか", "ありがとー。", "ゴメンね、", "ひきとめて。"]}, {"box": [126, 561, 174, 666], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["ううん、", "じゃあねー。"]}, {"box": [114, 842, 166, 957], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["気になって", "たんでしょ？"]}, {"box": [360, 832, 415, 968], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["何急に", "聞いてんのよ！！！"]}], "img_path": "156.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [624, 103, 703, 246], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["あの二人、", "付き合って", "ないんだってさ。"]}, {"box": [84, 51, 370, 71], "vertical": false, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["からかいと手の高ホさんは"]}, {"box": [139, 192, 189, 363], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["聞こえてたよ！！", "何のぞいてんのー！！？"]}, {"box": [617, 589, 716, 721], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["あーもう、", "絶対授業中に", "トイレ行きたく", "なるよー。"]}, {"box": [329, 571, 379, 677], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["行けば", "いいじゃん"]}, {"box": [638, 952, 736, 1047], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["コイツらと", "恋愛話は", "できそーに", "ないな．．．"]}, {"box": [380, 898, 462, 1031], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["授業中に", "トイレなんて", "恥ずかしいよ！！"]}, {"box": [353, 1123, 462, 1167], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["おわ"]}, {"box": [148, 922, 200, 1057], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["私もついてって", "あげるから"]}], "img_path": "157.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [86, 48, 421, 154], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["俺の妹に絶対に"]}, {"box": [578, 38, 699, 119], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["山本崇"]}, {"box": [556, 73, 832, 219], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["新型ラブコメもう１作！！！", "崇一朗"]}, {"box": [603, 219, 761, 234], "vertical": false, "font_size": 15.0, "lines": ["まぁわかりましゃ。笑っちゃってたよ。"]}, {"box": [96, 365, 144, 773], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["ちょっぴりキケン．．．？"]}, {"box": [152, 290, 324, 594], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["リボンほどけば", "妹のホンネは"]}, {"box": [219, 439, 263, 676], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["素直で凶暴、"]}, {"box": [436, 244, 465, 379], "vertical": true, "font_size": 29.0, "lines": ["山本崇一朗"]}, {"box": [487, 849, 788, 943], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["山本崇一朗", "ｓＯＩＣＨＩＲＯＹＡＭＡ誰のＴＯ－ＰＲＥＳＥＮＴＳ"]}, {"box": [7, 735, 493, 1143], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["キョッ"]}, {"box": [485, 1135, 604, 1151], "vertical": false, "font_size": 16.0, "lines": ["ゲッサンＳＳＯＳ"]}, {"box": [499, 1064, 805, 1128], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["絶賛配信中！！"]}], "img_path": "158.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [615, 209, 735, 234], "vertical": false, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["札月キョーコ"]}, {"box": [421, 101, 552, 164], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["－＆ｃスト"]}, {"box": [319, 176, 527, 218], "vertical": false, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["ＴｕｄａｔｓｕｋｉｎｏＫｙｏｋｏ．Ｃｈａｎ", "Ｃｈａｒａｃｔｅｒ８：８ｔｏｒｙ"]}, {"box": [113, 205, 221, 236], "vertical": false, "font_size": 29.0, "lines": ["札月ケンジ"]}, {"box": [687, 287, 704, 342], "vertical": true, "font_size": 17.0, "lines": ["お兄ちゃん"]}, {"box": [504, 444, 698, 481], "vertical": false, "font_size": 16.0, "lines": ["◆普段はクールだが、", "リポンが取れると凶暴＆素直化"]}, {"box": [570, 513, 694, 596], "vertical": false, "font_size": 17.0, "lines": ["つ想いを寄せる", "日々野さんにも", "「シスコン」呼ばわり", "されるが、実は．．"]}, {"box": [502, 297, 520, 346], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["ゴメンね。"]}, {"box": [468, 519, 509, 576], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["札月君ですっ！", "シスコンだし"]}, {"box": [279, 331, 309, 388], "vertical": true, "font_size": 12.0, "lines": ["おはこれが"]}, {"box": [317, 537, 342, 581], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["そんなんだからシスコンって言われんのよ。"]}, {"box": [146, 354, 155, 393], "vertical": true, "font_size": 12.0, "lines": ["お姉たな。"]}, {"box": [115, 444, 303, 461], "vertical": false, "font_size": 12.0, "lines": ["皆が恐れるシスコンヤンキー"]}, {"box": [188, 539, 215, 610], "vertical": true, "font_size": 13.0, "lines": ["オレはシスコン", "じゃねぇえ！！"]}, {"box": [119, 539, 136, 584], "vertical": true, "font_size": 17.0, "lines": ["いや．．．シスコンだろ。"]}, {"box": [530, 698, 710, 738], "vertical": false, "font_size": 14.0, "lines": ["９彼の妹キョ一コは人の血を", "吸う怪力のキヨンシーであり。"]}, {"box": [343, 828, 501, 933], "vertical": false, "font_size": 16.0, "lines": ["●札の役割である", "リポンがほどけてしまうと、", "本能のままに人を", "襲ってしまう。おまけに", "素直になってしまうのだ"]}, {"box": [286, 805, 304, 845], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["ありがとうお兄ちゃん。"]}, {"box": [112, 691, 363, 752], "vertical": false, "font_size": 16.0, "lines": ["つ妹に近づ〈男を片っ端から威圧すること", "から、校内最強の「シスコンヤンキー」と", "恐れられるれ月ケンジ"]}, {"box": [127, 802, 164, 863], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["すごく素直になる。"]}, {"box": [197, 1000, 793, 1123], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["かわいいボンスと．．．", "２０１３．．．ここで『一般ビフォーアフター！！"]}, {"box": [73, 1051, 191, 1079], "vertical": false, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["ＰＯＩＮＴ"]}], "img_path": "159.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [131, 93, 602, 142], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["からかい上手の高ホさんの"]}, {"box": [134, 180, 567, 203], "vertical": false, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["ゲッサン少年サンデーコミックススペシャル"]}, {"box": [197, 527, 219, 550], "vertical": false, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["著"]}, {"box": [193, 413, 516, 439], "vertical": false, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["２０１４年６月１７日初版第１刷発行"]}, {"box": [404, 522, 664, 619], "vertical": false, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["山本県一朗", "ＣＳＳｉｃｈｉｒｏｙａｎａｍａｎｏｎｏ．２０１４", "上位", "たとえば"]}, {"box": [438, 384, 759, 399], "vertical": false, "font_size": 15.0, "lines": ["ＩＳＢＮ９７８－４－－０９－１２５０１５－５"]}, {"box": [195, 594, 264, 623], "vertical": false, "font_size": 29.0, "lines": ["発行者"]}, {"box": [197, 636, 262, 657], "vertical": false, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["印刷所"]}, {"box": [147, 847, 236, 873], "vertical": false, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["発行所"]}, {"box": [135, 696, 556, 833], "vertical": false, "font_size": 17.6, "lines": ["「ゲッサン」２０１３年７月号別冊付録〜２０１４年５月号別冊付録、", "「選用少年サンデー」２０１４年第３号掲載作品", "連載担当／高長佑典", "単行本編集責任ノ星野文彦", "単行本編集ノ高長佑典「三輪基子（アイプロダクション）"]}, {"box": [408, 638, 619, 655], "vertical": false, "font_size": 17.0, "lines": ["中央精版印刷株式会社"]}, {"box": [257, 844, 602, 860], "vertical": false, "font_size": 16.0, "lines": ["〈〒１０－８００１）東京都千代田区一ツ橋二の三の"]}, {"box": [425, 861, 743, 918], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["クロロン編集は「２０１５年に編集のパスターマンス」の", "第１８条第一の第二条第条第６６条例第１５条第十十六条第二十八条第三条第八号館・東京都大学館"]}, {"box": [139, 921, 760, 1150], "vertical": false, "font_size": 16.0, "lines": ["●並木には十分注意しておりますが、印刷、製本など製造上の不備がございましたら「両作局コール", "センター「ブリーダイヤルのみ」３０年６月２３日にご連絡ください。", "〈電話受付は、上・日「提供日を続く９：３０－１７：８０", "このように、というのは、●本書の一部あるいは全部を無視であ．．．。教要事故、上演、放送等をすることは、法律で認められた場合を除き、", "著作者および出版者の権利の侵害となります。あらかじめ小松あで詐諾をお求めください。", "国｛公益社団法人日本複製権センター委託出版物", "本書を無断で被災被要（コピー）するここでは、著作権法上の例外を除き、禁じられています。本書をコピー", "される場合は、事前に公益社団法人口本複製権センター一口ＲＣの治療を受けてください。", "ＰＲＲＣ（Ａｌｄ）／ｗｗｗｉｔｃｏｒｉｎ．セメール・ＴＶＤで「Ｉｎｄｅｒｔｅｒｉｃｅ」のＴＥＬ．Ｑ８－３０１－２８２", "●本書の電子データ化等の無断複製は著作権法上での例外を除き禁じられています。", "代行業者等の第三者による本書の電子的複製も認められておりません。"]}], "img_path": "160.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [132, 839, 179, 887], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["ちきっ"]}, {"box": [120, 814, 196, 917], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.666666666666668, "lines": ["名名行", "著発", "昔、"]}, {"box": [214, 814, 723, 946], "vertical": false, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["からかい上手の高木さん", "山本崇一朗", "株式会社小学館", "〒１０１－８０１１東京都千代田区一ツ橋２－３－１"]}, {"box": [124, 994, 571, 1018], "vertical": false, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["電子書籍制作会社株式会社昭和ブライト"]}], "img_path": "161.jpg"}]}